\v 8 ‚ÄúN…® oragh! Men n…®ghn…®ziba gavgaviz…® mogh…®n, k…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zim damight…® a gavgavigham. Ez…® men naviba gavgaviz…® mogh…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n navim damight…® a men damazibar gavgavigham.  
\v 9 K…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zim damight…® n…® daimon…®n dag…®am…®n m…®n gavgavigham. Eght…® n…® men ganganibar gan…®va d…®gavir kuram damu men atiatingan mark…®. Me bar akaba batozir adarasi.‚Äù 
