\v 18 Eght…® gumazitam arazir kurabar amight…®, k…® aremeghs…® a m…®k…®mam, eght…® n…® ikiangs…®zir akam…®n a m…®k…®m suam, a navim giragh uan arazir kuraba ategh, angam…®ra ikiam. N…® a m…®kemeght…®, a uan arazir kurabagh iraghan kogh, ovegham. N…® a m…®kemeghan koght…®, an arazir kuraba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® an oveght…®, an ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim n…®n ikiam.  
\v 19 Egh n…® uab…®, n…® arazir kurabagh amir gumazir kam m…®kemeght…® an arazir kuraba atagh…®raghan aghuagh aremegham. A uab…® uan arazir kuraba bang…®n aremegham. Eght…® n…® an ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim ateran kogham. Egh arazir kam…®n, n…® uab…® uan ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n akuragh, ovengan kogham. 
