\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Esekiel 18:24; 33:12-13\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazir aghuitam uan arazir aghuim ategh arazir kuram damight…®, k…® an tuavim ap…®right…®, an aremegham. N…® dughiar kam…®n ikiangs…®zir akam a m…®kemeghan koght…®, a uab…® uan arazir kuraba bang…®n aremegham. A faragha amizir arazir aghuiba, k…® dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. An aremegham. Eght…® an ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim n…®n ikiam.  
