\v 26 \x - \xo 3:26 \xt Esekiel 2:5-7; 24:27; Luk 1:20-22\x*Eght…® k…® n…®n m…®zem damight…®, an anang n…®n akar averiam ap…®right…®, n…® m…®k…®man asagham. Eght…® n…® uam akaba batozir ik…®zir kam, n…® me ak…®rs…® me m…®k…®man kogham.  
