\c 4  
\ms1 Esekiel akam akura ghaze, Jerusalem ikuvigham 
\mr (Sapta 4--24) 
\s1 Apaniba Jerusalem gas…®ghas…®gham 
\p  
\v 1 Egha God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® mang…® brigh…®n tam inigh nguazim dat…®gh, egh Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n nedazim brigh…®n kam osiriz…® mogh…®n an aghoregh.  
\v 2 Egh brigh…®n kam…®n borogh…®n, n…® mati m…®dorozir gumaziba nguibar ekiar mam av…®nigh a m…®sogh a iniamin arazibar ababaniba, n…® bar dar ar…®kigh. Egh daghurim…®n ababanim damight…® a nguibar ekiar kam bar anev…®nigh, egh nguazibagh kuva nguibar ekiar kam…®n d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n dar pozibav k…®nigh. Eght…® da danganir aghuir m…®dorozir gumaziba is…®n ghuavanang tuiv ik…® m…®soghamibar m…®n ikiam. Egh m…®dorozir gumaziba ik…® m…®soghamin averpeniba nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n dar ababaniba ar…®kigh. Egh nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim ginivt…® an akarighir…®s…®, me temer bar ekiaba inigh da is…® akuriabar arigh, egh dagh afughafuzir ababanibar mogh…®n, n…® bar mogh…®ra dar ababanim nguazim…®n dar amu.  
\v 3 Egh n…® dar ababaniba arigh g…®vagh, ain…®n itaritam inigh anek…®righ a is…® n…® uab…® ko nguibar ekiam…®n tong…®n anesaragh, egh n…® uan guam nguibar ekiam m…®tuagh, egh nguibar ekiar kam bagh m…®sogh a iniamin ababanim damu. Eght…® Israelian gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n gan fogham, g…®n m…®dorozir gumazitaba iz…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4-5 ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n damigh g…®vagh, egh ragh uan agharir k…®riam mogh…®n m…®togh, 390plan dughiabar ir…®gh…®v ik…® arazir kurar Israelia amizibar os…®mt…®zibar ivezir kuram ateram. K…® 390plan dughiaba n…® gan…®ngi, ez…® dughiar kaba Israel…®n ik…®zim os…®mt…®zir me ini ikiamim, a 390plan azenibar d…®bobonim ko magh ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® bar dughiar ruarir kam…®n me amizir arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim iniam.  
\v 6 N…® kamagh…®n damigh g…®vagh, namba 2…®n dughiam…®n ua m…®togh. Egh n…® uan agharir guvim mogh…®n m…®togh egh ir…®gh…®v ik…®, egh Judan gumazamiziba amizir arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim…®n ivezir kuram ateram. K…® 40plan dughiaba n…® gan…®ngi, ez…® dughiar kaba Judabar ik…®zim…®n os…®mt…®zir me ini ikiamin azenibar d…®bobonim ko magh ghu. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúN…® ir…®gh…®v ik…®va, apaniba Jerusalem iniasava amir ababanir nedazir itibar gan. Egh n…® mati m…®dorozim damuasava ami mogh…®n damu, egh nan akam is…® kamagh…®n pamtem an gun m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòNguibar ekiar kam ikuvigham.‚Äô  
\v 8 N…® orakigh, k…® benir gavgavim…®n n…® ikeght…® n…® uab…® gigh…®vk…®n…®s…® damuva avegham. N…® kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®, dughiar k…® n…® gan…®ngizir kaba, da mang…® bar g…®vagham. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, wit…®n igharagha gari taba ko, balin taba ko, nguezir igharagha garir taba inigh…®va bar mogh…®ra da is…® itarir ekiatam dat…®gh, dagh asegh da veregh ua bagh bret…®n tabar ingarigh da tuegh. N…® 390plan dughiar kabar uan agharir k…®riam…®n ofizibara ir…®ghv…®ra ik…®va darara dam…® ik…®.  
\v 10 Egh dagher aruer vam…®ran n…® damamin os…®mt…®zim, 200pla gremra tu, a tong ua s…®vazir puvat…®.  
\v 11 Egh uaghan d…®par n…® aruer vam…®ra damamim a 1 litara tugh, a tong uam afiraghan mark…®.  
\v 12 Egh n…® bret tus…® gumazir buariba inigh dar ar…®kigh. Buariba m…®s…®ngight…®, n…® da inigh dar avim at…®gh bretba tu. N…® gumazamizibar damazim…®n bizir kabar amut…®, me n…® amir bizir kabar ganam.‚Äù 
