\v 13 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúArazir n…® amir kaba, kar Israelia damuamin arazibar ababaniba. K…® g…®n apanibar amamangat…®ght…®, me mang…® Israelia ko m…®sogh…®va me inigh kantrin igharazim…®n mang…®gham. Eght…® me kantrin igharazim…®n ik…® dagher nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zibar amam.‚Äù 
