\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Ofa Gami 17:15; Aisaia 65:4; Esekiel 20:49; Aposel 10:14\x*Ez…® k…® an akam ikaragha ghaze, O Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, ‚ÄúN…® orakigh! K…® kamagh…®n damighan kogham. Bar puvat…®. K…® uan igiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, n…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Egha as…®zir atiaba m…®sozir as…®ziba ko, uari ariaghirir as…®zibar tuziba, k…® uan akam…®n tam amezir puvat…®. Egha dagher n…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®ziba, k…® uan akam…®n tam amezir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® a nan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúMamagh…®n, k…® n…®n amamangar…®si, n…® gumazir buariba ategh egh bulmakaun buaribara inigh avim at…®gh bretba tu.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Egha a ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® oragh! K…® Jerusalem…®n daghebar amight…® da bar otevegham. Eght…® gumazamiziba atiatim sara, aruer vam…®rara men tughat…®ghamin damamin daghebara ikiam. Eght…® gumazamizibar d…®pabar daghem, k…® anetught…®, me arueba vaghvagh dughiar vam…®ran d…®pam am…® bar osemegham.  
