\c 5  
\s1 Esekiel uan dapanir ar…®zim gise 
\p  
\v 1 God ua kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® mang…® m…®dorozir sabar bar ghumt…®zir tam inigh resan m…®n an suiragh uan ghuamas…®zim ko dapanir ar…®ziba bar adagh isegh. Egh ar…®zir kaba bar da is…® skel dat…®gh dar os…®mt…®zim g…®fogh, egh 3plan pozibar da tuiragh da ar…®kigh.  
\v 2 Egh 390plan aruebar g…®n ivezir kurar kam g…®vaght…® n…® d…®kafigh. Eght…® arazir kam kamagh…®n Israelian akagham, apaniba Jerusalem inigha g…®fa. N…® d…®kavigh uan ar…®zir pozir faragha itim inigh, Jerusalem…®n akazir ababanim gamir brigh…®n kam gis…®n dat…®gh, a daboroght…® a isi. Egh ar…®zir pozir namba 2 inigh, brigh…®n kam…®n m…®riam daruva da akun, uan m…®dorozir sabam…®n tintinibar ada aghor mang…®. Egh ar…®zir pozir namba 3 inigh da akunight…®, am…®nim da ater tintinibar mang…®. Eght…® k…® uan m…®dorozir sabam inigh ar…®zir kabar g…®nt…®gh mangam.  
\v 3 Egh n…® ar…®zir vabara ateght…® da ik…®t…®, n…® da inigh uan azenan itir korotiam…®n m…®riam gitorogh da isamigh.  
\v 4 Egh ar…®zibar tong…®n, n…® ua taba inigh avim m…®k…®night…® da isi. Eght…® dar avim isi mang…® Israel…®n ik…®zim gir…®gh, bar mogh…®ra men isigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gan, k…® a isa kantrin igharazibar nguibabar tong…®ram anet…®. Ez…® me bar an okarigha iti.  
\v 6 Ez…® Jerusalemia, bizir k…® damuasa me m…®kemeziba ko arazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n zuir puvat…®gha, me amir arazir kuraba, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba amir arazir kuraba bar dagh afira. Me bar ak…®rim ragha bizir k…® damuasa me m…®kemezibagh asaragha, nan arazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 7 Bizir kam bang…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Jerusalemia, ia oragh! Ia arazir k…® ifongeziba batuegha bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemezibar g…®n zuir puvat…®gha, kantrin ian borogh…®n itiba men arazibagha ami. Ez…® arazir kurar ia amiba, kantrin igharaziba amir bizir k…® damuasa m…®kemezibar arazir kuraba bar dagh afira.  
\v 8 Bizir kam bang…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® ghaze, nan agorogetam tong ian itir pu. Bar puvat…®. K…® ian apanim…®n m…®n iti. Egh kantrin igharazibar damazibar, k…® ian araziba tuis…®ght…® gumazamiziba bar ian ganam.  
\v 9 Ia arazir k…® ifongezir puvat…®zir bar av…®ribagh amigha g…®fa. Ez…® k…® ivezir kuram ia dan…®ng…®va arazir fom…®ra amizir puvat…®zir kaba, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia damuam. Egh k…® ua g…®n kamagh…®n ia damighan kogham.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Ofa Gami 26:29; Azir Akam 4:10; Esekiel 6:8; Amos 9:9; Sekaraia 7:14\x*Eght…® arazir kurar ia amizibar ivezir kuram, ia ameboghfeziaba uan boribav sogh…®va dar tuzibar am…®t…®, boriba uan ameboghfeziabav sogh men tuzibar amam. K…® paz…®v…®ra ia damuam, eght…® ariaghirezir puvat…®zir darasi, k…® me aghamsight…® me tintinim…®n nguazir kam…®n danganir igharazibar mangegham. 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara ikia uan ziam…®n guizbang…®ra m…®gei. Ia arazir kurar k…® ifongezir puvat…®zir av…®riba, nan D…®penim…®n aven dagh amiz…® nan D…®penim nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Eght…® k…® ian apangkuv ian asughasuighan kogham. Ia mati gumazim uan dapanir ar…®zim bar a gise. Kamagh…®ra, k…® guizbang…®ra bar ia gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 12 K…® ia is…® 3plan okoruabar ia arigham. Eght…® namba 1…®n okoruam, m…®tiriar ekiam ian agh…®t…® ar…®mariaba ia damut…® ia nguibar ekiam…®n aven ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® namba 2…®n okoruam, apaniba iz…® nguibar ekiam…®n azenan m…®dorozir sababar me m…®soght…® me ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® namba 3…®n okoruam, k…® me aghamsigh tintinim…®n me amangight…® me nguazim…®n danganiba bar dar mangeght…®, k…® apanibar amamangat…®ght…® me uan m…®dorozir sababa inigh men ag…®nt…®gh mang…® me m…®sogh…®rar…®gham. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúEgh k…® kamagh…®n damight…® nan adarir ekiam ko an…®ngagharim g…®vagham. Bizir kaba otivt…®, ia nan akam g…®n…®ghn…®gh fogham, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® asetam…®n amamangat…®ght…®, a nan danganim inighan kogham.  
\v 14 K…® ia gas…®ghasight…®, kantrin igharazir ian borogh…®n itibar gumazamiziba iz…® ian gan kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòMevzika! Me bar mogh…®ra ikufi. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men arazir kuraba ikarvagha me gas…®ghas…®ki.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, nan an…®ngagharim ia bagha bar nan ekefe, ez…® k…® bar pazav…®ra ia damu ia gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® arazir kam kantrin igharazir ian borogh…®n itibar gumazamizibar damazim…®n ikiangs…®zir arazim…®n m…®n otogham. Eght…® me ian ganigh atiatigh n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuam. Egh me d…®bovir akabar ia m…®k…®mt…® ia bar aghumsigham.  
\v 16 Egh k…® ian dagher damamibar amight…®,\f + \fr 5:16 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* da bar oteveght…®, m…®tiriaba puv ian agham. Eght…® m…®tiriar aghazir kam, mati me baribar ia gasima, ia m…®zazir ekiaba isi mogh…®n uari baragham.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Akar Mogomem 6:8\x*Egh k…® m…®tiriar aghazir ekiam ia bagh anemadagh, as…®zir atiabar amamangat…®ght…®, da ian boribav sogh…®rarigham. Egh k…® ar…®mariar bar kurabar amamangat…®ght…® da ia bagh izam. Egh k…® apaniba amadaght…®, me iz…® bar ia m…®sogh…®rarigh ia ag…®vagham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 6  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God  // gumazamizir asebar g…®n zuibar atari 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israel…®n kantrin m…®ghs…®abar amadaghan gan…®va nan akam…®n gun dav k…®m,  
\v 3 egh suam, Ia Israel…®n kantrin m…®ghs…®aba ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam…®n akam baragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, uan akam isa ia m…®ghs…®ar ekiaba ko m…®ghs…®ar doziba, ko daghurir ekiaba, ko danganir zariba, ia gan…®di! A ghaze: K…® apanibar amamangat…®ght…® me iz…®, gumazamiziba asebar ziaba fer danganir p…®n itiba bar dagh as…®ghasigham.  
\v 4-5 Egh apaniba, ian ofa gamir dakoziba, ko ian ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim gamibar dakoziba bar da ap…®rarigham. Egh k…® apanibar amut…®, me Israelian gumazamiziba bar me m…®sogh…®rarigh, men kuaba ian marvir guabar damazibar da akunight…®, da iregh…®v ikiam. Eght…® k…® apanibar amamangat…®ght…®, me men aghariba ian ofa gamir dakozir kabar m…®riabar tintinibar da aghamsight…® da iregh…®v ikiam.  
\v 6 Egh apaniba, Israel…®n nguibar ekiaba bar dagh as…®ghasight…® da ikuvigham. Eght…® men m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir ia asebar ziaba feba ko, men ofa gamir dakoziba ikuvigh pura ikiam. Eght…® ian asebar marvir guaba me bar dagh as…®ghasigham. Egh mughuriar aghuim zuir ofa gamir dakoziba bar da akararight…®, Israelia amir arazir kurar kaba bar mogh…®ra g…®vagham.  
\v 7 Eght…® apaniba Israel…®n kantrin averiam bar a daru, egh gumazamizibav sogh…®rar…®gham, eght…® ariaghirezir puvat…®gha angam…®ra itiba ganigh kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 6:8 \xt Aisaia 6:13; Jeremaia 30:11; 44:14; 44:28; Esekiel 7:16\x*‚ÄúK…® tarazi ateght…®, me ik…®v…®ra ikiam. Eght…® tarazi m…®dorozim…®n tintinibar aregh mang…® kantrin igharazibar ikiam.  
\v 9 Me saghon itir kantrin igharazir kabar kalabus…®n ik…®, na g…®n…®ghn…®gh kamagh…®n fogh suam, me uan navir averiabar aven ak…®rim ragha na gasara, ez…® arazir kam bar na ab…®ra. Me uan damazir kurabar aseba bagha pamtem garava, bar dagh ifonge, ez…® arazir kam na gamima, k…® bar me baseme. Me fo, me arazir kurar k…® ifongezir puvat…®zir av…®ribagh ami. Eght…® me uan arazir kurar m…®z…®r…®zir amiziba bagh bar aghumsigham.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt Jeremaia 5:12-14; Esekiel 6:7\x*Egh me kamagh…®n fogh suam, K…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. Egh me fogham, Akar Gavgavir k…® amizim, a purama akar k…®nim puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uan dafaribav sogh, pamtem…®n dagaribar nguazim d…®k…®va, osemez…® mogh…®n kamagh m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòMevzika! Israel…®n ik…®zim, me arazir kurar k…® ifongezir puvat…®zir av…®ribagh ami.‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®, apaniba iz…®va men tarazi, bar me m…®sogh…®rarigham. Eght…® men tarazi, m…®tiriaba ko ar…®mariaba me damut…®, me ar…®ghiregham.  
\v 12 Men tarazi saghon ik…® ar…®mariaba bang…®n ar…®mighiram. Eght…® tarazi rogh…®ra ik…®t…® apaniba iz…® me m…®soght…® me ar…®mighiram. Eght…® angam…®ra ikiav…®ra iti darasi, m…®tiriar ekiam men agh…®t…® me ar…®m…®ghiregham. Kamagh…®ra, k…® men an…®ngaghegh bar ivezir kuram me dan…®ngam.  
\v 13 Eght…® apaniba, Israelian gumazamizibar marvir guabar ofa gamir dakoziba, ko m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir asebar ziaba feba, ko temer ekiabar apebaba, ko me aseba bagha ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim gamir danganibar Israelian tabav sogh…®raright…®, men kuaba pura tintinibar iregh…®v ikiam. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, Israelia arazir kam…®n gan fogh suam, k…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 14 K…® uan agharim men nguazim…®n anemadaght…® a bar mogh…®ra ikuvigham. K…® not…®n amadaghan Diplan nguibam…®n ikegh mang…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir saut…®n itim…®n otogh, men nguaziba bar dar amight…®, da gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganibar m…®n ikiam. K…® men nguibatam ateght…® a ikian kogham. Da danganir k…®nibar m…®n ikiam. Eght…® gumazamiziba derav…®ra na g…®fogh suam, k…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\c 7  
\s1 God Israelia ag…®vam 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh na m…®gei:  
\v 2 O nguazir kam…®n gumazim, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n Israel…®n nguazibar itir gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze: 
\b  
