\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Akar Mogomem 7:3; 9:4; 14:1\x*egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam bar an averiam daruva gumazamizir men namakaba amir arazir kurar God aghuazibar osemegha itiba, n…® me bativ, men guaba osizirir ababanim me dar…®gh.‚Äù 
