\v 13 \x - \xo 12:13 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:7; Jeremaia 52:11\x*Eght…® k…® uan ivem aguraght…® an an suiragham. Egh a inigh Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®gham, kar Kaldiabar nguazim. Eght…® a nguazir kam…®n ganighan kogham.\f + \fr 12:13 \ft Dughiar kabar g…®n, Babilonia, Atrivim Sedekaian suiragha egha a inigha a is…® kalabus dar…®ghasa Babilon…®n ghu. Me a gamiz…®, an damazimning okafi. Ez…® arazir kam…®n akar is…®n zuir kam a guizbang…®ra oto. Egha a bar uan damazimning…®n Babilon…®n nguazim…®n ganizir puvat…®, egha a nguazir kam…®n areme. N…® eghaghanir kam, 2 Atriviba 25:7 ko Jeremaia 52:11, an gan.\f* Egh a nguazir kam…®n ik…® mang…® aremegham.  
