\p  
\v 21 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 22 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, bizir tizim bagha Israelian gumazamiziba zurara akar otevir kam gami? Me ghaze, ‚ÄòAkam inigha izir gumaziba bizir g…®n izamibav g…®a ghaze, da otivam. Ez…® azenir av…®riba iza zui, irebabar m…®n garir bizir kabar aven otivir akaba guizbang…®ra otivir puvat…®gha pura zui.‚Äô Ez…® k…® Israelian aghuzir akar kam…®n aghua.  
\v 23 N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®k…®masa. Aghuzir akar me zurara m…®geir kam k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n aneg…®vagham. Me Israel…®n kantrin aven uam a m…®k…®man kogham. N…® kamagh me m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòDughiam otogha g…®fa. Eght…® irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar akaba, da vaghvagh guizbang…®ra otivam!‚Äô 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, akam inigha izir gumazir maba Israel…®n gumazamizibar tong…®n ikia irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar gara, akar ifavariba ko apezeperir akavsiabar gun me m…®gei. Eght…® k…® Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n aven bar arazir kam ag…®vagham.  
\v 25 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® Israelia me ko m…®k…®mam. Eght…® bizir k…® m…®kemeziba, da zuam…®ram otivam. Ia akaba batozir ik…®zim, ia oragh! Ia aremeghan kogh ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, k…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damuam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 26 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh na m…®gei,  
\v 27 ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazim, Israel…®n ik…®zim ghaze, ‚ÄòEsekiel, irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar gara, egha g…®n otivamin bizibar m…®g…®r…®g…®abar gun m…®gei. Ez…® bizir a m…®geir kaba dat…®r…®gh…®n otivan kogham. Puvat…®, da bar g…®n otivam.‚Äô  
\v 28 Eght…® n…® me m…®k…®m suam, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam me ikaragha ghaze, K…® sughsughan kogham. Bizir k…® m…®kemeziba, da dat…®r…®gh…®n otivam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa!‚Äù 
\c 13  
\s1 God, akam inigha izir gumazir ifavaribar atari 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® mang…® Israel…®n akam inigha izir gumazibav k…®m. Men marazi uan n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n ghua, g…®n otivamin bizibar gun m…®gei. N…® pamtem…®n men atar me m…®k…®m. N…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam barakigh.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei: Akam inigha izir gumazir onganir kaba, Mevzika! Me bar ikuvigham! Me irebabar m…®n garir bizibar garir puvat…®. Me uari uan navir averiabar aven itir bizibar g…®n ghua, uan n…®ghn…®zibar dav gei.  
\v 4 O Israelian gumazamiziba, ian akam inigha izir gumaziba, mati afiar atiaba nguibar ekiar ikuvizir mam puram a garui.  
\v 5 Me nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir akaraghirezir danganibar gara ua dar ingarir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Izamin Dughiar Ekiam…®n m…®dorozim otoght…®, ia Israelia tuivigh gavgavighan kogh apanibav soghan iburagham.  
\v 6 Akam inigha izir gumazir ifavarir kaba, me irebabar m…®n garir bizibar aven itir biziba, da bizir ifavariba. Me g…®n otivamin bizibar m…®g…®r…®g…®abav gei, ez…® da guizbang…®ra puvat…®. Me ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akabav gei. Ez…® puvat…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me amadazir puvat…®. Egha me ti manmagh…®n n…®ghnigha ghaze, men m…®g…®r…®g…®abar dagheba otivam? Bar puvat…®gham. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®k…®masa, ia irebam…®n m…®n amizir bizir ia gariba, da guizbang…®ra puvat…®. Ez…® g…®n otivamin bizir ia m…®geiba, da akar ifavariba. Ia ghaze, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba. Ez…® puvat…®. K…® akatam ia m…®kemezir puvat…®!  
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ian m…®g…®r…®g…®aba guizbang…®ra puvat…®. Ez…® ia irebam…®n m…®n garir biziba, da gumazamizibagh ifari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia ko itir puvat…®gha, navim ia bagha bar ikufi.  
\v 9 Ia akam inigha izir gumazir ifavariba irebam…®n m…®n garir bizibar gara akar ifavaribagh amua, egha g…®n otivamin biziba deraghav…®ra gumazamizibagh eghari puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® paz…®v…®ra ia damigham. Nan gumazamiziba uari akuvagh ik…®t…®, ia men tong…®n ikeghan kogham. Eght…® ian ziaba uaghan Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n osirizir ziabar aven ikian kogham. Eght…® ia ua Israel…®n nguazim…®n izeghan kogham. Egh ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 13:10 \xt Jeremaia 6:14; 8:11\x*\x - \xo 13:10-12 \xt Aposel 23:3\x*‚ÄúIa akam inigha izir gumazir ifavariba, ia ifara nan gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, men dabirabim bar dera. Ez…® guizbang…®ra men dabirabim bar derazir puvat…®! Nan gumazamizibar dabirabim mati, gumazim d…®vazim…®n ingariz…® a guizbang…®ra deragha gavgavizir puvat…®. Ez…® ia akam inigha izir gumazir ifavariba izava, d…®vazir kurar kam pen…®n ghurghurim a gaghui. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®vazir kam…®n azenan itir ganganim bar dera. Ez…® puvat…®. A guizbang…®ra ir…®gh ikuvigham.  
\v 11 N…® mang…® gumazir pen…®n ghurghurim…®n aghuizir gumazir kabav k…®m suam, men d…®vazim akarighir…®gham. K…® amozir iz…® mamagh…®ra ikiamim amadagham. Eght…® amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba a gis…®n iram, eght…® am…®nir gavgavim a givangam.  
\v 12 Eght…® d…®vazim ir…®ght…®ma, me bar ian azangs…®gham, ‚ÄòD…®vazir kam bar gavgavizir puvat…®! Ian pen…®n ghurghurim tong d…®vazim…®n akurazir puvat…®. Ia e gifari.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, nan an…®ngagharim…®n, k…® amozir iz…® mamagh…®ra ikiamim, ko amozir of…®zir ekiar dag…®abar m…®n gariba, ko am…®nir gavgavim amadaght…®, da d…®vazir kam gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 14 D…®vazir ia pen…®n ghurghurim…®n aghuizir kam, k…® anekararigh, an d…®vazir m…®ngarim…®n aven itir dag…®aba aghamsight…® da pura tintinibar ikiam. A degeghir…®gh bar ia m…®sogh…®rarigham. Eght…® ia bar fogh suam, k…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúKamagh…®ra, d…®vazir kam ko gumazir d…®vazim pen…®n ghurghurim aghuzir kaba, me nan an…®ngagharim…®n gavgavim baragham. Eght…® k…® ia m…®k…®m suam, d…®vazim a itir puvat…®, kamagh…®ra, te pen…®n ghurghurim a gaghui, me uaghan ikian kogham.  
\v 16 Akam inigha izir gumazir ifavarir manaba, irebabar m…®n garir bizibar gara, Jerusalem m…®g…®a ghaze, an dabirabim bar dera, ez…® guizbang…®ra an dabirabim bar derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® adagh as…®ghas…®ki. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 God amizir imezibagh amibar atari 
\p  
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israelian amizir imezibagh amibar atar, me zurara g…®n otivamim bizibar gun m…®geir kabav gei. Akar me m…®geir kaba me uan n…®ghn…®zibar dagh ami. N…® nan akam inigh mang…® me m…®k…®m.  
\v 18 N…® me m…®k…®m suam: Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIavzika! Ia amizir kuraba, ia g…®fa! Ia akavsiar kuraba bagha daveriabar ingara da isava gumazamizibar agharibagh azui. Egha akavsiabar amuamin iniba isamigha da isa men dapaniba ave. Gumazamizir oteviba ko ruariba, ia kamagh…®ra bar mogh…®ra me gami. Eght…® me bizir kaba uari dar…®gh gavgavim inigh gumazamizir igharazibagh ativaghasa. Ia amizir kaba uarira uarigh n…®ghnigha, gumazamizir maba paza me gamua marazi deragha me gami. Ia ghaze, arazir ia amir kam ti dera? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 19 Ia nan gumazamizibagh ifara ghaze, ia ziar ekiam na gan…®di. Ez…® puvat…®, ia nan ziam ab…®rav…®ra iti. Ia akuzir arazim gamua gumazamizir mabav sozi me ariaghiri, egha marazir akurvasi. Gumazir k…® ovengan ifongezir puvat…®ziba, ia me m…®sozi me ariaghiri, egha k…® ovengasa ifongezir gumazamiziba ia deragha me gami. Ez…® gumazamiziba ian arazir kam bagha bar ifongegha bret…®n oteviba ko balin muziaribar ia givezima, ia arazir kurar kabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 20 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Ia oragh! Ia akavsiar kuraba bagha daveriabar ingara da isava gumazamizibagh ativaghasa men agharibagh azui. Mati gumazim ruarim…®n kuaraziba buri mogh…®n ia gumazamizibagh ami. Ez…® k…® daveriar kaba bar dagh ifongezir puvat…®. Ia agharibagh aghuizir daveriar kaba, k…® bar da aghoreght…®, ia uam akavsiabar amuan kogham. Eght…® gumazamizir ia ativazir kaba ua ian apengan ikian kogham.  
\v 21 Egh k…® uaghan akavsiabar amuamin inir ia gumazamizibar dapaniba aveziba adegham, eght…® nan gumazamiziba f…®righ…®regh ua ian apengan ikian kogham. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 22 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòIa akar ifavarir bar av…®ribagh amua, gumazamizir aghuibar n…®ghn…®zibagh as…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® k…® uab…® me gamiz…®, me osemezir puvat…®. Ia gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibav g…®a, gavgavim me gan…®dima me uan navibagh ighasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rim inighan kogham.  
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia ua irebabar m…®n garir bizir ifavaribar ganan kogham. Eght…® g…®n otivamin bizibar apezeperir akar ia amiba, da bar g…®vagham. Eght…® k…® uan gumazamizibar akuragh ua ia da me inight…®, ia ua me gativagh men ganan kogham. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\c 14  
\s1 Gumazamiziba asebar ziaba fan, God aghua 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar mam Israelian gumazir dapanir maba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghasa nan azangs…®ghasa izi.  
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 3 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, gumazir kaba uan naviba isa asebagh an…®ngiz…®, arazir kam bang…®n men arazir kuraba ghua bar ekefe. Me bar uan asebagh ifongegha da atagh…®raghan aghua. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n pura iza n…®ghn…®ziba bagha nan azangs…®si. Eght…® k…® guizbang…®ra men azangs…®zim ikarvaghan aghua.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® me m…®k…®m suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n tong…®n gumazitam uan navim is…® asebar anigam, eght…® arazir kam bang…®n an arazir kuraba mang…® bar ekeveght…®, a uan aseba bar dagh ifongegh da atagh…®raghan aghuagh, a pura iz…® n…®ghn…®ziba bagh God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n azangs…®gham, eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan ikarvazim kamak…®n, k…® fo, a ziar ekiaba aser av…®ribagh an…®di.  
\v 5 Aser kaba Israel…®n ik…®zim gamiz…®, me ak…®rim ragha na gasara. Ez…® nan ifongiam kamak…®n, k…® ua men navir averiaba iniasa n…®ghn…®si, eght…® me na baghv…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, n…® Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ia navibagh iragh, uan aseba ak…®rim ragh dagh asaragh, arazir kurar k…® bar aghuaziba da atakigh. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúEght…® Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n gumaziba o amiziba, o Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir uan kantri ategha iza Israelia ko itiba, ak…®rim ragh na gasaragh uan navim is…® asebar anigam, eght…® arazir kam bang…®n men arazir kuraba mang…® bar ekeveght…®, me uan aseba bar dagh ifongegh da atagh…®raghan aghuagh, egh me pura iz…® n…®ghn…®ziba bagh nan akam inigha izir gumazim…®n azangs…®gham, eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® men ikarvazim me dan…®ngam.  
\v 8 K…® men apanim damu, egh uan gumazamizibar tong…®n me batuegham. Eght…® ia Israelia bizir k…® me gamizir kam…®n ganigh, egh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamizir ak…®rim iragha a gasiba, arazir kam…®n me gami.‚Äô Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…®rara k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir kamagh garitam iz…® nan akam inigha izir gumazitam apezeper a damut…®, an akatam a danigham, bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim mati, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® nan akam inigha izir gumazim gifaraz…® an akar kam a gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ivezir kuram a dan…®ng…®va Israelian gumazamizibar tong…®n a batuegham.  
\v 10 Eght…® nan akam inigha izir gumazim ko, gumazir nan ifongiam g…®fofoghasa ghuava an azarazim, aning uaghara ivezir kurar magh garim iniam.  
\v 11 K…® kamagh…®n damigh, Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n tuavim ap…®right…® me uam ak…®rim ragh na gasan kogham. Egh arazir kurabar amuan kogh nan damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. Eght…® me nan gumazamizibara ik…®t…®, k…® men God…®n ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 God vaghvagha gumazamizibar arazir kurabar gari 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 14:12-20 \xt Ofa Gami 26:14-35; 1 Atriviba 8:33-40\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 13 ‚ÄúNguazim…®n gumazim, kantrin tam…®n gumazamiziba arazir kuram damigh…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikiam koght…®, k…® uan gavgavim men akagh men daghebar amight…® da mang…® bar otevegham. K…® m…®tiriam azir dughiam me bagh anemadaght…®, gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba v…®rara daghem bang…®n ar…®ghiram.  
\v 14 Gumazir 3plan aghuir kaba, Noa, Daniel ko Jop, me kantrin kam…®n ikiai,\f + \fr 14:14 \ft Noan eghaghanim…®n akaba, Bar Faraghav…®ram Otivizir Bizibar Eghaghanim…®n Ak…®nafarim, sapta 6…®n ikegha ghua sapta 9…®n tu. Ez…® Jop…®n eghaghanim…®n akaba da Jop…®n Ak…®nafarimra iti. Ez…® Daniel…®n eghaghanim…®n akaba da Daniel…®n Ak…®nafarimra iti.\f* k…® 3plan gumazir kabagh n…®ghnigh egh gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar apangkuvighan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® gumazir 3plan kabara me ateght…® me deragh ikiam. Eght…®, gumazamizir igharaziba ar…®m…®ghiregham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúK…® maghsuegh, as…®zir atiaba amadaght…® da iz…® gumazamizibav sogh…®rar…®gham, egh nguazim damight…® atiatim bar anevaraght…®, gumazitam a daruan kogham.  
\v 16 Ez…® gumazir 3plan aghuir kaba, Noa, Daniel ko Jop, me kantrin kam…®n ikiav…®ra ikiai, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® angam…®ra itir God, k…® uan ziam…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® 3plan gumazir kabara n…®ghnigh men otariba ko guivibar apangkuvighan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® gumazir 3plan kabara me ateght…® me deraghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…®, gumazamizir igharaziba ar…®m…®ghiregham. Eght…® nguazim ruarir k…®nim…®n otogham. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEgh k…® maghsuegh, m…®dorozir sababar suighiz…® apaniba kantrin kam bagh me amadaght…®, me iz…® gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba uaghan bar me kuavaremegham.  
\v 18 Ez…® gumazir aghuir 3plan kaba kantrin kam…®n ikiav…®ra ikiai, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® angam…®ra itir God, k…® uan ziam…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® 3plan gumazir kabara n…®ghnigh, men otariba ko guivibar apangkuvighan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® gumazir 3plan kabara me ateght…® me deragh ikiam. Eght…®, gumazamizir igharaziba ar…®m…®ghiregham. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúEgh k…® maghsuegh, ar…®mariar kuratam amadaght…® a bar atamra kantrin kam g…®m…®right…®, k…® uan an…®ngagharim…®n gumazamiziba ko as…®zibav sogh…®rar…®gham.  
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir 3plan kaba, Noa, Daniel ko Jop, kagh ikiai. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® angam…®ra itir God, k…® uan ziam…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® 3plan gumazir kabagh n…®ghnigh men otariba ko guivibar apangkuvighan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® gumazir 3plan kabara me ateght…® me deragh ikiam. Eght…®, gumazamizir igharaziba ar…®m…®ghiregham. 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 14:21 \xt Akar Mogomem 6:8\x*‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® uan ivezir kurar 4plan kaba is…® Jerusalem…®n da amangam, kar m…®doroziba, ko m…®tiriam azir dughiam, ko as…®zir atiaba, ko ar…®mariar kuram. Eght…® da gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba uaghara me m…®sogh…®rarigham.  
\v 22 Eght…® varazira ik…®v…®ra ikiam, kar Israelian otariba ko guiviba. K…® g…®n men aku azenan izam, eght…® me ia bagh iz…®t…®, ia me amir arazibar gan. Men araziba bar ikufi. Eght…® n…® uan navir averiam…®n fogh suam, ivezir kurar k…® Jerusalem bagha amadazim, a vorogh…®ra ghu.  
\v 23 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogham, k…® amizir biziba da m…®ngarir aghuiba itima, k…® dagh ami. N…® men arazir kurabar ganigha fo, k…® me ikarvaghamin arazim bagh navir am…®rizim inigham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 15  
\s1 Wain…®n ikar…®zim…®n akar is…®n zuim 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei: 
\b  
\q1  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, 
\q2 n…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, wain…®n ikar…®zim, a ti derazir puvat…®. 
\q1 Wain…®n ikar…®zim…®n agharim, ruarir ar…®zim…®n temebar agharibar tong…®n manmagh…®n deragh aghung, 
\q2 dagh afiragham? 
\q3 Ti puvat…®. 
\q1  
\v 3 N…® a is…® bizitam…®n ingarigham, o? 
\q2 Egh n…® wain…®n ikar…®zir otevitam inigh, biziba guamin akezibar ingarigham, o? 
