\v 10 N…® oragh! Me wain…®n ikar…®zir kam nguazir aghuim…®n an opari. 
\q2 Eght…® a deraghv…®ra ik…®va aghungam, o? Ti puvat…®gham. 
\q1 Aruem anadi nagh…®n ikezir am…®nim iz…® a givangt…®, a imuigham. 
\q2 A danganir a faragha aghuimra, ik…® bar m…®sigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim 
\p  
\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 12 \x - \xo 17:12-13 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:15-20; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10-13\x*‚ÄúN…® mang…® Israel…®n ik…®zir akaba batozim…®n azaragh, me ti akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®fos, ti puvat…®? Akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu. Babilonian atrivim, Jerusalem…®n izegha atrivim ko an gumazir dapaniba ua bagha me inigha Babilon…®n ghu.  
\v 13 Babilon…®n atrivim, Judan kantrin ikiav…®ra ikiava, Judan kantrin atrivim…®n adarazir mav inigha a ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gami. A ghaze, gumazir kam, a Judan kantrin atrivir igiam…®n otogham. Egha ghaze, atrivir igiam an apengara ikiasa. Egha a Judan kantri ateghasa amua gumazir ziaba itiba, a me inigha kalabus…®n ghu.  
\v 14 Babilon…®n atrivim ghaze, atrivir igiam akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir kam…®n g…®n mangan aghuagh, a uan kantri damut…® a ua gavgavigh d…®kavigh Babilon m…®soghs…® damuam, eght…® Babilon…®n atrivim ua iz…® bar Judan kantri gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 15 Ez…® Judan atrivir igiar kam Babilon…®n atrivim…®n akam batuegha, Isip…®n atrivim bagha akam amadagha ghaze, a hoziaba ko m…®dorozir gumazir av…®ritaba amadaght…® me an akurvaghs…® izam. N…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, atrivir igiar kam derav…®ra ikiam, o? Puvat…®gham. A Babilon…®n atrivim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim ab…®ki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Babilon…®n atrivim iz…® pazav…®ram a damigham. 
\p  
\v 16 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra iti, k…® uan ziam…®n guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei: Judan atrivim mang…® Babilon…®n kantrin kalabus…®n ik…® mang…® aremegham. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Babilon…®n atrivim anem…®sevez…®, an atrivir igiam…®n iti. Egha a Babilon…®n atrivim ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gamua ghaze, an an apengan ik…®va bizibar amuam. Egha a uab…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim…®n aghuagha aneb…®ki.  
\v 17 Eght…® Babilonia iz…®, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ek…®arugh nguazim g…®ku d…®vazim borogh…®n dar pozibav m…®k…®nigham. Egh me nguazir pozir kabagh is…®n tuivigh ik…® m…®dorozim damuam. Me kamagh n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, gumazir av…®rim ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® Isip…®n atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir bar gavgavim, m…®dorozim…®n dughiam…®n iz…® men akuraghan kogham.  
\v 18 Ia oragh! Judan atrivir igiam, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim…®n aghuagha aneb…®ki. Egha a bizir kaba bar dagh ami. A dat…®r…®gh…®n ar…®mang…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra iti, k…® uan ziam…®n guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® atrivir kam ikaragh pazav…®ra a damigham. A guizbang…®ra nan ziam…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gami, egha aneb…®ki.  
\v 20 K…® an suiragham, mati gumazim as…®zibar suizir ivem onegha a m…®k…®niz…® an an suira. K…® a inigh Babilon…®n mang…® munagh an arazir ak…®rim ragha na gasarazim tuis…®gh, egh ivezir kuram a dan…®ngam.  
\v 21 An m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir aghuiba, me bar ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® m…®dorozir gumazir ikiav…®ra itir varazira, me tintinim…®n suaragh…®r…®gham, mati am…®nim iza ivaima biziba tintinibar ghue. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 God Israelian akuraghasa akam ak…®ri 
\q1  
\v 22-23 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei: 
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® uab…®, k…® sidan temer ruarim an aguar muziarir bar p…®n ititam atugham. 
\q2 Egh a inigh mang…® Israel…®n m…®ghs…®ar igharazir bar dagh afirazim…®n an anekaragham. 
\q1 Eght…® temer kam aghuigh ekevegh aguar ruariba ik…® b…®va, ov…®ziba ikiam. 
\q2 Egh a sidan temer bar dirim…®n otogh, sidan temer mabagh afiragham. 
\q1 Eght…® kuarazir guar av…®riba iz…® an aguabar dapighir…® aruem…®n uari apazam. 
\q2 Egh me an aguar kabar m…®konibar ingaram. 
