\c 18  
\s1 Gumazamiziba bar God vaghvagha men arazibar gari 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Jeremaia 31:29\x*‚ÄúIa manmaghsua zurara Israelian nguazim g…®n…®ghn…®gha aghuzir akar kam…®n a m…®gei? 
\b  
\q1 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòAfeziaba ko amebaba wain…®n ov…®zir angamt…®ziba api. 
\q2 Ez…® wain…®n ov…®zir kaba is…®ngt…®ziba puvat…®gha 
\q3 boribar akabav sozi men atariba me giri.‚Äô 
\b  
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra iti, k…® uan ziam…®n bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Israelia ia uarira uarir tong…®n aghuzir akar kam m…®k…®man kogham!  
\v 4 \x - \xo 18:4 \xt Esekiel 18:20; Rom 6:23\x*Ia oragh! Gumazamiziba bar men ik…®r…®m…®rim, nan bizim, afeziam ko amebam…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim ko borim…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim, nan bizim. Eght…® gumazir arazir kuram gamizim, anar…®ra aremegham. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúGumazitam ti bar deragh, arazir kuraba an puvat…®ght…®, gumazir kam deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 18:6 \xt Ofa Gami 20:18\x*Gumazir kam, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir aseba famin danganibar zuir puvat…®gha me bagha ofa gamua dar dagheba apir puvat…®gha, Israel…®n asebar marvir guabar ziaba fer puvat…®, egha gumazir igharazibar amuiba koma akuir puvat…®, egha uaghan amizir uan iak…®nibav sozim koma akuir puvat…®.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 18:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:25\x*Egha a igharaz darazi ab…®ra arazir kurabar me gamir puvat…®. Egha gumazir igharazibar biziba okeir puvat…®. Egha a uan namakam…®n amamangat…®z…®, a pura ada dag…®ar kaba ini, ez…® namakam ua da ikarvaghamin ababanim…®n m…®n a uan biziba isa a gan…®ngi. Egha g…®n namakar kam iza uan dag…®ar kaba ikarvaghasa, ez…® gumazir aghuir kam ua namakam…®n bizim a gan…®di. Egha gumazir aghuir kam, m…®tiriaba azir darasi, a dagheba isa me gan…®di. Egha korotiaba puvat…®zir darasi, a korotiaba isa me gan…®di.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 18:8 \xt Ofa Gami 19:15\x*Egha an namakam an dag…®aba pura da inigha ua da ikarvaghasa, an dag…®ar an an…®ngizim gis…®n ua dag…®aba isir puvat…®. Egha gumazamiziba kotiaba bagha izi, a guiz…®n arazim…®n g…®n ghua men kotiaba tuis…®si. Egha an arazir kurabar amuan aghua.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Ofa Gami 18:5; Esekiel 20:11; Amos 5:4\x*Gumazir kamagh…®n amim, an arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba baragha derav…®ra dar g…®n ghua dagh ami. Gumazir kam, nan damazim…®n dera, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an angam…®ra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir kam otaritam ik…®t…®, otarir kam gumazibav soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram, kar otarim…®n os…®mt…®zimra.  
\v 11 An afeziam arazir kabagh amir puvat…®, otarim uab…®ra arazir kabagh ami. A m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir aseba famin danganibar ghua da bagha ofa gamir dagheba api. Egha gumazir igharazibar amuiba koma akui. Egha dagher me aser marvir guaba bagha ofa gamiziba apava gumazir igharazibar amiba ko arazir kurar k…® aghuazibagh ami.  
\v 12 Egha a gumazamizir onganaraziba ab…®ra arazir kurabar me gami. Egha gumazir igharazibar biziba okei. Eght…® namakatam an dag…®ar a iniziba ikarvaghs…® iz…®t…®, gumazir kurar kam ua namakam…®n ababanir bizim a danighan kogham, a pura ua bagha a ini. Egha marvir guabar ziaba fe. Egha arazir kurar k…® aghuazir igharazibagh ami.  
\v 13 Egh an namakam an dag…®aba inigh, ua da ikarvaghs…®, an dag…®ar an an…®ngizim gis…®n, a ua dag…®ar igharaziba isi. Gumazir kam ti angam…®ra ikiam ti? Puvat…®gham. A ikian kogham. An arazir kurar k…® aghuazir kabagh ami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ovengam. A uab…® uan os…®mt…®zim bang…®n ovengam. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúEght…® gumazir kurar kam…®n otarim, uaghan otaritam ik…®t…®, otarir kam uan afeziam…®n gant…®, an arazir kurabar amuam. Eght…® a uan afeziam…®n m…®n arazir kurabar amuan aghuagham.  
\v 15 Egh otarir kam, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir aseba famin danganibar mangan kogh, da bagh ofabar amu, dar daghebar aman kogham. Egh gumazir igharazibar amuiba ko dakuan kogham.  
\v 16 Egh a igharaz darazi arazir kurabar me damuan aghuagham. Egh gumazir igharazibar biziba ok…®man aghuagham. Egh a uan namakam…®n amamangat…®z…®, a pura ada dag…®ar taba inigh, eght…® namakam ua da ikarvaghamin ababanim inian aghuagham. Egh gumazir aghuir kam, m…®tiriaba azir darasi, a dagheba is…® me dan…®ngam. Egh korotiaba puvat…®zir darasi, a korotiaba is…® me dan…®ngam.  
\v 17 Egh an namakam an dag…®aba pura da inigh, egh ua da ikarvaghs…®, an dag…®ar an an…®ngizim gis…®n ababanim inighan kogham. Egh an arazir kurabar amuan aghuagham. A bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba baragh derav…®ra dar g…®n mang…® dar amuam. Otarir kam, uan afeziam…®n arazir kurabar os…®mt…®ziba inigh, da bang…®n aremeghan kogham. Puvat…®gham. An angam…®ra ikiam.  
\v 18 An afeziam bar arazir igharagha garibagh ami. A ifara biziba ok…®ava zurara arazir kurabar igharaz darazigh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…® uan arazir kurar an amizibagh ipurigh aremegham. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúEz…® ia kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄòTizim bagha, otarim afeziam…®n arazir kurabar ivezir kuram inian kogham?‚Äô Ez…® ian azangs…®zim…®n ikarvazim kamak…®n. An otarim nan arazir aghuiba ko arazir k…® ifongezibar suiragha derav…®ra dar g…®n zui, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an aremeghan kogh derav…®ra ikiam.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 18:20 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:16; Aisaia 3:10-11; Esekiel 18:4; Rom 2:9\x*Gumazim an arazir kuram gami, anar…®ram aremegham. Otarim afeziam…®n arazir kurabar ivezir kuram inian kogham. Eght…® afeziam, otarim…®n arazir kurabar ivezir kuram inian kogham. Gumazir arazir aghuim gamizim, an an ivezir aghuim iniam. Eght…® gumazir arazir kurabagh amim, a da bang…®n ivezir kuram iniam. 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Esekiel 18:27; 33:12; 33:16-19\x*‚ÄúGumazir arazir kurabagh amitam arazir kuraba ategh arazir k…® ifongezibar suiragh arazir aghuibar amuam, an aremeghan kogham, an angam…®ra ikiam.  
\v 22 A dat…®r…®gh…®n arazir aghuibagh ami. Egha a faragha amizir arazir kuraba k…® da g…®n amada, egh ua dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an angam…®ra ikiam.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 18:23 \xt Esekiel 33:11; 1 Timoti 2:4; 2 Pita 3:9\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei. Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba ariaghiri, k…® bizir kam bagha bar akongezir pu. Puvat…®. K…® kamaghsua, me navibagh iragh angam…®ra ikiasa k…® ifonge. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 18:24 \xt Esekiel 3:20; 33:12-13; 33:18; 2 Pita 2:20\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazir aghuitam arazir aghuiba ategh, arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko arazir kurar k…® aghuazibar amu, egh an angam…®ra ikian kogham. A faragha amizir arazir aghuitam, k…® tam gin…®r…®ghan kogham. An ak…®rim ragha na gasara, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan arazir kuraba bang…®n ovengam. 
\p  
\v 25 ‚ÄúO Israel…®n ik…®zim, ia zurara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòEkiam amir arazir kaba, da derazir puvat…®.‚Äô Israelia, ia derav…®ra nan akam baragh. Ia ghaze, nan araziba ti ikufi. Bar puvat…®. Iarara ian arazibara bar ikufi!  
\v 26 Gumazir aghuitam, arazir aghuim ategh arazir kuram damigh an os…®mt…®zim ikiam. Egh a uan os…®mt…®zir kam bagh an ovengam.  
\v 27 Eght…® gumazir kuratam, arazir kuram ategh arazir aghuim damu, an aremeghan kogham. A deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 28 An arazir kurar amizir kam g…®fogha g…®vagha, anetegha arazir aghuim…®n g…®n zui. Bizir kam bang…®n, an aremeghan kogham. An angam…®ra ik…® deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
