\v 30 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze, O Israel…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazamiziba, k…® vaghvagh bar ian araziba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia navibagh iragh, ia amir arazir kuraba ategh, ak…®rim ragh dagh asaragh. Eght…® ian arazir kuraba ia gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham.  
