\v 4 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® men arazir kurar me amiziba bagh akam me gas…® me tuis…®gham. N…® me is…® azenara me at…®gh me tuis…®gh. N…® men inazir afeziaba amizir arazir bar kurar k…® aghuazibar gun me m…®k…®m.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 20:5-6 \xt Ua Me Ini 6:2-8\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® me m…®k…®m. K…® Israelia ginabazir dughiam…®n, k…® Jekop…®n ik…®zim…®n ovavir boriba ko Akar Gavgavim ak…®righa uab…® isa men aka. Dughiar kam…®n, me Isip…®n nguazim…®n itima, k…® uab…®n gun me m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® ian God.  
