\v 15 \x - \xo 20:15 \xt D…®boboniba 14:26-35\x*Egha k…® gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua me m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® me inigh nguazir k…® me bagha inabazim…®n mangan kogham. Nguazir kam bar deragha, nguazir otevir maba bar dagh afira. Nguazir kam bar deraz…®, dagheba an ikia bar deraghav…®ram aghui.  
