\v 29 Egha k…® men azangs…®si, ‚ÄòIa manmaghsua ghua m…®ghs…®ar kabar ghuavanaga asebar ofa gami?‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia, fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n danganir ofa gamir kaba kamagh…®n dar bori, ‚ÄòP…®n Itir Danganiba.‚Äô 
