\v 37 ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n danganir kam…®n mati, sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim uan sipsipbagh eghuva asadivim suiraz…® sipsipba an apengan iti an ada medi mogh…®n, k…® ia gativagh ia damight…®, ia nan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim baragham. Eght…® k…® bar deraghv…®ra vaghvagh ian araziba bagh ia tuis…®gham.  
\v 38 Ian tong…®n itir akaba batogha arazir kurabagh amir gumazamiziba, k…® me batueght…®, me ua ian tong…®n ikian kogham. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n kantrin igharazibar nguazibar ikia kalabuziam…®n iti, eght…® k…® dar me inigh azenan izam. Eght…® me ua Israel…®n nguazim…®n aven mangan kogham. Eght…® ia kamagh fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 39 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® dat…®r…®k…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, O Israel…®n ik…®zim, ia ti na baraghan aghuagh, egh ia vaghvagh dat…®r…®gh…®n pura ik…® mang…®, uan ifongiabar g…®n mang…® uan asebar ziaba f…®. Egh ia asebar ofa damut…®, ian ofan arazir kam ua nan ziar zuruzim ab…®nan kogham. 
\p  
\v 40 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, kotiar kam g…®vaght…®ma, ia nan gumazamiziba bar uamategh Israel…®n nguazim…®n mang…® nan m…®ghs…®ar ruarir bar p…®n ghuavanabozir kam…®n mang…® nan ziam fam, eght…® k…® bar ia gakuegham. Ia uan ofaba ko, ian bizir ia ifongegha faragha at…®ziba ko, ian bizir bar aghuir na baghav…®ra itiba, ia na bagh ada inigh iz…® na dan…®ngt…® k…® bar akuegham.  
\v 41 Ia tintinim…®n kantrin igharazibar ghuegha dar aven itiba, k…® ia inigh azenan iz…®, egh k…® mughuriar aghuim zuir ofaba bagha bar akongez…® mogh…®n, k…® ia bagh navim deragh bar akuegham. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, bizir k…® ia gamir kabar ganigh kamagh…®n fogh suam, nan araziba bar zue.  
\v 42 K…® ia inigh Israel…®n nguazim…®n izam, kar nguazir k…® ian inazir afeziabar an…®ngasa akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamizim. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 43 Eght…® ia uan arazir kurar ia amiziba ko, arazir ia uari uari gamua nan damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zibagh in…®r…®gham. Ia amizir arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kaba bang…®n, ia bar uarir ikuragh suam, e bar ikufi.  
\v 44 O Israel…®n ik…®zim, k…® uan ziar aghuim bang…®n deragha ia gami. K…® ian arazir kurabar ivezir kuram isa ia gan…®ngizir puvat…®. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
