\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® munagh Jerusalem…®n gan…®va kamagh…®n Israel…®n nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba akam me gas…® me m…®k…®m suam, me arazir kurabagh amir ik…®zim. Gumazamiziba asebar ziaba fer danganiba, k…® uaghan dagh ifongezir puvat…®.  
\v 3 N…® nan Akar Gavgavim is…® kamagh…®n Israel…®n nguazim…®n itir gumazamizibav k…®m suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze, k…® ian apanim damuva, uan m…®dorozir sabam…®n bar ia m…®sogh…®rarigham, ian gumazamizir aghuiba ko kuraba sara.  
\v 4 Guizbang…®ra, k…® ian gumazamizir aghuiba ko kuraba uaghara me m…®soghs…® saut…®n amadaghan ikegh uan m…®dorozir sabam…®n me m…®sogh mang…® not…®n amadaghan tugham.  
\v 5 Eght…® gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® uan m…®dorozir sabam an m…®sevim…®n anesigha g…®fa, egh k…® uam a is…® anerugham kogham. Puvat…®. K…® bar puv…®ra ia damigham.‚Äù 
