\v 6 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® mang…® gumazamizir kabar kuabat…®gh…®n azenara tugh tiarim akar arang, mati n…®n d…®ghorim b…®ghasava ami.  
\v 7 Eght…® me ti n…®n azaragham, n…® tizim bagha tiarim akarava arai? Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam, ia bativamin bizim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am izegha g…®fa. Dughiar kurar kam, iz…® otoght…®, atiatim ian navibagh iz…®vaght…®, ian agharapaniba ian am…®raght…® ia gavgaviba puvat…®ght…®, ian sueba in…®gh…®va akongam. Ia deraghv…®ram oragh, dughiar kuram otivasav ami. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 9 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® g…®n izamin bizim…®n gun gumazamizibav k…®m suam: 
