\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan gumazamiziba os…®mt…®zim me danigh men ganigham, me navibagh iraghan koght…®, bizir kaba me bativam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa. 
