\q3 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\s1 Babilonian atrivim iz…® Jerusalem m…®sogham 
\p  
\v 18 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 19-20 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, Babilonian atrivim uan m…®dorozir sabam suiragh izamin tuavir pumuning am…®sefe. Tuavir kamning uaghara kantrin vam…®ran ikegh izam. N…® tuavir akar kamning…®n bizitam osirigh anesaragh. Eght…® atrivim iz…® an ganigh fogham, tuavir mam Amonian nguibar ekiam Raban zui. Tuavir akar igharazim, a kantri Judan nguibar ekiam Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 21 Eght…® Babilon…®n atrivim iz…®va tuavir akamning…®n n…® osirigha asarazir bizim…®n m…®riam…®n m…®t…®gham. Egh a tuavir manamra mang…®s…® fofoghs…®, faragh uan barir pibar m…®dorozir akavsiabar amu, uan afuzir m…®zebagh ivivamang dagh inobagh inobagham. Egh a uan afuzitam Raban akagh, egh tam Jerusalem…®n akakagham. Eght…® atrivim afuzir vam…®ra iniam. A uaghan asebar azangs…®ghs…®, ofa gamizir as…®zir d…®ghorim…®n gan…®va anesavsuigham.  
\v 22 Ez…® afuzir atrivim uan agharir guvim…®n suirazim, barir pim…®n afuzim Jerusalem…®n akaght…®, a fogh me m…®k…®m suam, me mang…® Jerusalem…®n m…®dorozim damuam. Egh me Jerusalem…®n itiar akabar aven mang…®s…®, me temer bar ekiaba inigh da is…® akuriabar arigh, dagh afughafugham. Egh m…®dorozir gumaziba tiariba akar…®va, temer bar ekiar kaba inigh mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n itiar akaba akaram. Egh Jerusalem kons…®, nguazibagh kuva nguibar ekiar kam…®n d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n dar pozibav k…®nam. Eght…® da danganir aghuir m…®dorozir gumaziba is…®n ghuavanang tuivigh ik…® m…®soghamibar m…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 23 ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n gumazamiziba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, bizir kam a guizbang…®ra puvat…®. Me fo, me fom…®ra Babilonian atrivim ko akar d…®k…®r…®zibagh amua ghaze, me an apengan ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ghaze, m…®dorozitam me bativan kogham. Ez…® puvat…®. Babilon…®n atrivim, men arazir kuraba bang…®n akam me gas…®, men suigh me is…® kalabus dar…®gham. 
\p  
\v 24 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® Israelia ian m…®k…®masa, ian arazir kuraba aghua ghua bar ekefe. K…® ian arazir kurar kaba g…®n amadaghan kogham. Ia arazir kurar kaba azenara dagh ami, ez…® gumazamiziba ian arazir kurabagh fo. Os…®mt…®zir ekiam ian iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia is…® ian apanibar agharim dar…®gham. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 25 ‚ÄúN…® Israel…®n atrivim, 
\q2 n…® nan akaba batogha arazir kurabaram amir gumazim, 
