\v 27 As…®ghas…®gham, as…®ghas…®gham! 
\q1 Guizbang…®ra, k…® nguibar ekiam gas…®ghasight…® a bar ikuvigham. 
\q2 As…®ghas…®zir arazir katam fom…®ra nguazim…®n otoz…®, gumazitam an ganizir puvat…®. 
\q1 Nguibar kam pura ik…® mang…® gumazir k…® inabazim…®n dughiam…®n otogham. 
