\c 22  
\s1 Jerusalemia arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamiziba, gumazamizir av…®rim…®n m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® me is…® kotiam dat…®gh me tuis…®gham, o? N…® bigh…®v…®ra me amir arazir m…®z…®r…®zir k…® aghuazibar gun me m…®kemeght…®, me fogham.  
\v 3 Egh n…® nguibar ekiar kam m…®k…®m suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam k…® ghaze, ia Jerusalemia uari uan gumazamizir av…®rim m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha ia uari bagha marvir guabar ingara dar ziaba fava, egha ia uari kamagh…®n amigha nan damazim…®n m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ia gas…®ghas…®ghamin dughiam rogh…®ra ize.  
\v 4 Ia gumazamizibar ghuzibagh amiz…®, da ire, egha marvir guabar ingarigha nan damazim…®n m…®ze, ez…® arazir kurar kabar os…®mt…®zim ian iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ian dughiam izegh g…®fa! Arazir kam bang…®n, k…® kantrin igharaziba bar men amamangat…®ght…®, me ian aghums…®zim…®n gan…®va ia d…®pov ian ingaravakam.  
\v 5 Kantrin ian borogh…®n itiba ko kantrin saghon mar itiba ian gara fo, ia arazir bar kurabagh amir gumazamiziba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ian ingaravati. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúIa oragh! Ian tong…®n itir Israelian gumazir dapaniba bar uari uan gavgaviba fava igharaz daraziv suaghar…®si.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 22:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:12; 22:21-22; God…®n Araziba 5:16; 24:17\x*Ian aven itir gumazitam tong derav…®ra uan ameboghfeziabar akaba baragha men apengan itir puvat…®. Kantrin igharazibar gumazamizir ian tong…®n itiba ia me ab…®ri. Egha ian tong…®n itir amizir odiarir paba ovengeziba, ko ameboghfeziaba ariaghirezir boriba, ia men biziba isa pazav…®ra me gami.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 22:8 \xt Ofa Gami 19:30; 26:2\x*Ia ghaze, nan ziam fer biziba, da pura biziba. Egha ia Sabat…®n arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®gha aneb…®ragha ghaze, a pura dughiar k…®nim. 
\p  
\v 9 ‚ÄúIan gumazamizir maba, akar ifavaribar igharaz darazigh amua me m…®sogh…®rar…®ghasava ami. Ez…® ian marasi, asebar ofa gamir dagheba api. Ez…® marasi, zurara uan inivaf…®zir agorogebar arazim…®n g…®n ghua aghums…®zir arazibagh ami.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 22:10-11 \xt Ofa Gami 18:7-20\x*Ez…® ian marasi, uan afeziabar amuiba koma akui. Ez…® marasi, amizir uan iak…®nibav sozir dughiabar me ko arazir kurabar amuasa me gakaghori.  
\v 11 Ez…® marazi poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gami. Ez…® igharaziba uan otaribar amuiba koma akui. Ez…® marasi, uan afeziabar guiviba koma akui.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 22:12 \xt Ua Me Ini 22:25; 23:8; Ofa Gami 25:36-37; God…®n Araziba 16:19; 23:19\x*Ez…® ian gumazamizir maba, iveziba isa ghua igharaz daraziv suaghar…®si. Ez…® marasi, uan namakabar dag…®aba pura da inigha ua da ikarvaghs…® an dag…®ar an an…®ngizim gis…®n ua dag…®aba ini. Ez…® marasi, uan namakar gumazibagh ifara me gami me atiatima, me me da dag…®aba isa bizir av…®riba iti. Ia bar na g…®n amadagha na g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúIa gan! Ia ok…®mak…®abagh ami darasi, ko igharaz daraziv suaghar…®zi darasi, k…® ian an…®ngaghe, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ivezir kuram ia dan…®ng uan dafaribav sogham.  
\v 14 Dughiar k…® pazav…®ra ia damuamin kam…®n, ia uan navir averiabar aven os…®mt…®zir kam ater…®va puv…®ra atiatingam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® damuam.  
\v 15 K…® ian gumazamiziba inigh tintinim…®n kantrin igharazibar me aghamsigham, eght…® arazir kuraba dutugh mang…® g…®vagham.  
\v 16 Eght…® kantrin igharaziba ian gan…®va ian aghuagh m…®k…®m suam, ia pura bizir k…®nim. Eght…® ia uari fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\s1 God…®n an…®ngagharim mati avir ekiam 
\p  
\v 17 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 18 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, Israel…®n ik…®zim, k…® bar men am…®ra. Me mati gumaziba silva iniasa dag…®aba avir ekiam…®n m…®nem…®n aven da tuema, da amera egha em…®ra dar muziarir kurar ingangariba puvat…®ziba iri. Ez…® me da isa da makuni.  
\v 19 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia nan ikiangs…®zir akam derav…®ra a baragh. Ia silvabar m…®n amir puvat…®, ia mati dar muziarir kurar ingangariba puvat…®zir kaba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bar mogh…®ra ia akuvagh ia inigh mang…® Jerusalem…®n nguibar torimra m…®zazim ia gasam.  
\v 20 Nan adarim ko an…®ngagharim mati avir ekiam. Gumaziba silva iniasa avir ekiam…®n dag…®aba m…®nem…®n da tue mogh…®n, k…® ia tuam. Me dag…®aba akuvagha avim givima a pamten isima, dag…®aba amera d…®pam…®n m…®n em…®ra iri mogh…®n, k…® ia akuvagh ian atar ian an…®ngagham.  
\v 21 K…® ia inigh ia akuvagh m…®zazim ia gasegham. Guizbang…®ra k…® bar ian an…®ngaghe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, nan an…®ngagharim avir ekiam…®n m…®n bar ian isigham. Eght…® ia ameregham.  
\v 22 Egh ia mati silva m…®nem…®n aven avir ekiam…®n isia ameri mogh…®n, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n nan gavgavim gan…®va derav…®ra na g…®fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® uan an…®ngagharim ia gingegha m…®zazim ia gase.‚Äù 
\s1 Israel…®n gumazir dapaniba arazir kurabagh ami 
\p  
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n na m…®gei.  
\v 24 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israelia m…®k…®m suam, me arazir kurar av…®ribagh amiz…®, men nguazim nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® bar men an…®ngaghe, egh m…®zazim me gas…®s…® amozim amadaghan kogham.  
\v 25 Gumazir dapanir ian tong…®n itiba mati, laionba as…®zim m…®suegha an kuam…®n m…®riam dazera an tuziba asiaghar…®gha da api. Me gumazamizibar dag…®aba ko men bizir aghuiba isi. Egha uan namakabav soghez…® me ariaghire. Men arazir kam…®n, amuir av…®rim paba puvat…®gha odiaribar iti.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 22:26 \xt Ofa Gami 10:10\x*Men ofa gamir gumaziba, nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuir puvat…®gha da ab…®ki. Egha ghaze, nan ziam fer biziba, da pura biziba. Egha me fozir puvat…®, bizir tizim bar zue, ez…® bizir manam nan damazim…®n pura bizim. Egha nan damazim…®n zuezir biziba ko bizir m…®z…®r…®zibar gun gumazamizibar sure gamir puvat…®. Me bar mogh…®ra Sabat…®n arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Egha me uarir uan tong…®n nan ziam ab…®ragha ghaze, nan ziar ekiam a pura bizir k…®nim. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúIan gumazir aruaba, mati afiar atiaba as…®zim m…®suegha uarir tong…®n an kuam getuima, a d…®ghoraghire. Me bizir av…®riba ikiasa gumazibav suaghar…®gha, egha ifara pura men biziba isi.  
\v 28 Akam inigha izir gumazir ifavariba, me gumazibar arazir kurar kaba moga mati gumaziba b…®rim, pen…®n ghurghurim a gaghui. Egh irebam…®n m…®n garir bizir ifavaribar garava, g…®n otivamin bizir ifavaribav gei. Guizbang…®ra, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® akatam me m…®kemezir puvat…®. Ez…® me ifara ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam…®n akam m…®gei.  
\v 29 Nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamiziba, uan namakabagh ifara biziba okei. Egha zurara arazir kurabar onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibagh amua pazav…®ra me gami. Egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir men tong…®n itiba ab…®ra men biziba okei, egha me guiz…®n arazim ategha kotiam…®n aven men tuavim ap…®ri. 
\p  
\v 30 \x - \xo 22:30 \xt Onger Akaba 106:23; Jeremaia 5:1; Esekiel 13:1-7\x*‚ÄúK…® gumazir men tong…®n itir kamagh…®n garitam, a bagha ruia an apizir puvat…®. Tinara nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bagh nan damazim…®n tugh…®va, nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir akaraghireziba ak…®ram. Eght…® k…® nguibar kam gas…®ghasighan kogham. K…® kamagh…®n damuamin gumazitam…®n apizir puvat…®.  
\v 31 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, men arazir kurar me amiziba bang…®n, k…® uan an…®ngagharim avim…®n m…®n a isa me gingegha me gas…®ghas…®ki. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\c 23  
\s1 Amizir pumuning,  // tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazibagh ami 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei.  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, guivir pumuning iti. Amebar vam…®ra aning bate.  
\v 3 Guivir kamning uan igiamra ikia Isip…®n kantrin ikia, derav…®ra itir arazim ategha tuavibar amizim…®n arazim…®n g…®n ghua pura tintinim…®n gumaziba ko ikarara uan m…®karzimning isa me gan…®di.  
\v 4 Avenemebam, an ziam Ohola, a Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ababanim gami. Ez…® an afumim…®n ziam Oholiba, a Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ababanim gami. K…® uaghara aning…®n iti, ez…® aning nan boriba bati. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúOhola, a nan amuimra, egha a pura tintinim…®n gumaziba koma akuir arazir kam bagha bar ikuvigha, Asirian m…®dorozir gumaziba, a bar me gifongegha zurara me bagha an m…®karzim d…®kava me baghav…®ra iti.  
\v 6 Asirian m…®dorozir gumazir kaba, me gumazir aruar ziaba itiba, ko m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba, egha me korotiar bar aghuir bluplaba azui. M…®dorozir gumazir igiar kaba hoziabagh is…®n apiav ikia m…®sosi. Ohola gumazir igiar kabar marvir guaba sara gari me an damazim…®n bar deraz…®, an navim me bagha d…®kaviz…®, a me ko arazir kuram gami.  
\v 7 An Asirian kantrin faragha zuir gumazir igiaba, men tuavir amizim…®n m…®n otoz…®, an agoroger kam a gamima, me a ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh ami. Egha an Asirian marvir guabar ziaba bar da fava, egha uan arazir kam bang…®n a m…®ze.  
\v 8 A uan igiamra Isip…®n ikia tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazir kam, a gamuav…®ra iti. Dughiar kam…®n, gumaziba a koma akua a ko ikararaima, a uan m…®karzim isa me gan…®ga ghuav…®ra iti.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® a isa, Asirian gumazir a bar ifongegha, me baghav…®ra itibar agharim gat…®.  
\v 10 Ez…® me an korotiam suez…®ma, a bibiabara iti. Egha me m…®dorozir sabam…®n Ohola m…®soghez…® ana aremez…®, me an guiviba ko otariba bar me ini. Ez…® amizir tintinibar itiba, Ohola batozir arazir kam…®n eghaghanim baregha sighsirir akabar n…®m…®ra, kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄòA uan arazir kurabar ivezim ini.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 11 ‚ÄúAn afumim Oholiba garima, arazir kam Ohola batoz…®, a bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®zi pu. Bar puvat…®. An arazir pura tintinibar gumaziba koma akuir kam gamuav…®ra iti, an arazir kuraba bar Ohola amizir arazir kurabagh afira.  
\v 12 A uaghan Asirian gumazir dapaniba ko, ziaba itiba ko, m…®dorozir gumazibar m…®dorozir korotiar aghuiba azuiba ko, gumazir hoziabagh is…®n apiav ikia m…®soziba, a me baghav…®ra ikia bar me gifonge. Gumazir kaba bar, me gumazir igiar bar diriba.  
\v 13 K…® kamagh…®n an arazir kam…®n garima, a bar ikuvigha, uan avenemebam…®n m…®rara ghu. Aning…®n araziba bar m…®ze. 
\p  
\v 14 ‚ÄúOholiba arazir kurar kabagh amua ghuav…®ra iti. A Babilonian gumazir aruabar nedazibar gari, me b…®rim…®n pen…®n aghevim…®n men nedazibar ingarigha da aghefe.  
\v 15 Egha dar ivariabar letiabar da am…®gh…®ni, egha iniba isa uan dapanibagh ikez…® dar otevir muziariba guighav iti. Oholiba Babilonian gumazir aruar kabar nedazibar gari da bar an damazim…®n deraz…®,  
\v 16 an navim d…®kaviz…®, a magh…®ra Babilonian gumazir kaba bagha akam amadagha ghaze, Kaldian kantrin gumaziba iz…®va a ko dakuam.  
\v 17 Ez…® Babilonia izava a ko poroghamiba uari koma akuava amir arazir kurabagh ami. Men agorogem me gami me an g…®n ghua arazir kurar igharazibar a gamiz…® a bar m…®ze, ez…® a men aghuagha ak…®rim ragha bar me gasara.  
\v 18 Oholiba bibiamra ikia azenara arazir kurabagh ami, ez…® gumaziba bar a g…®fo, an amizir bar kuram. Ez…® k…® an avenemebam…®n aghuaz…® mogh…®n, k…® an aghuagha ak…®rim ragha a gasara.  
\v 19 Ez…® a tintinim…®n gumaziba koma akuir arazir kam gami an ek…®va ghuavanagav…®ra iti, mati a faragha Isip…®n igiamra ikia tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazir kam gami.  
\v 20 An navim arazir kurar kam bagha puv a d…®kafi. Guizbang…®ra, gumazir kabar m…®karzir mogomeba bar ekevegha mati donkin am…®nas…®ziba, ez…® a da baka. Men am…®nas…®zibar d…®paba mati hoziabar am…®nas…®zibar d…®paba. 
\p  
\v 21 ‚ÄúOholiba, n…® Isip…®n guivir igiamra ikiava amizir arazir kaba bagha bar ifonge. Dughiar kam…®n gumaziba n…®n otemning gikararava n…® koma akui.‚Äù 
\s1 God Oholiba gas…®ghasigham 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Oholiba, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® fo, n…® ifongezir gumaziba, n…® bar men aghuagham. Eght…® k…® me damight…® me adarim n…®n ik…®, egh tintinibar ikegh iz…® paz…® n…® damu n…® gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 23 K…® Babilonia ko Kaldian gumaziba bar, ko Pekotia ko, Soaba ko, Koaba ko, Asirian gumaziba bar, me akuvagh me inigh izam. Me gumazir igiar diriba, ko gumazir ziaba itiba, ko gumazir dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumaziba, me bar hoziabagh is…®n dapiaght…® k…® me inigh izam.  
\v 24 Me m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir ekiam ko karisba ko biziba aterir dakoziba sara not…®n amadaghan ia m…®soghs…® izam. Me orar ekiaba ko orar doziba ko m…®dorozir dapanir asuaba inigh uarir p…®gh iz…® bar n…® ek…®arugham. K…® n…® is…® men agharim dat…®ght…®, me uan arazibar g…®n mang…® bizir me n…® damuasa m…®kemezibar g…®nt…®gh ivezir kuram n…® dan…®ngam.  
\v 25 K…® n…®n atara n…® bagha nan muriam bar kufi, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® me ateght…®, me uari uan an…®ngagharim…®n n…® damuam. Me n…®n atinim ko kuarimning atugh, egh n…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiamin adarasi, me m…®dorozir sabam…®n me m…®sogh…®rarigham. Bar guizbang…®ra, me n…® da n…®n otariba ko guivibar suight…®, gumazamizitaba ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…® me angam…®ra me dapongt…® me isiam.  
\v 26 Me n…®n korotiaba bar da surarigh n…®n bisba ko ring…®n diriba inigham.  
\v 27 N…® tuavim…®n amizim…®n araziba ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zir n…® fom…®ra Isip…®n nguazim…®n ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n amiziba, k…® bar ada ag…®vagham. Eght…® n…® uam asebar ziaba fan kogh, egh ua Isipia g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan! K…® n…® is…® gumazir n…® ifongezir puvat…®zibar agharim dat…®ght…®, me iz…® paz…® n…® damigham.  
\v 29 Gumazir kaba, bar n…®n aghua, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me n…®n bizir n…® ingara iniziba bar da inigh…®va, n…® ateght…®, n…® bibiamra ikiam. Mati n…® fom…®ra arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amua tuavim…®n amizim…®n m…®n bibiamra ike.  
\v 30 N…® kantrin igharazibar arua men asebar ziaba fava tuavim…®n amizim…®n m…®n amua, uab…® uab…® gamigha nan damazim…®n m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…® damut…®, n…® os…®mt…®zir kaba iniam.  
\v 31 N…® uan avenemebam…®n diarir nozibar g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® a gan…®ngizir ivezir kurar kav…®n iz…®vazir kam, k…® a is…® n…® dan…®ngight…® n…® anemam.  
\v 32 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® bar pazav…®ra n…® damigham, 
\q2 k…® paza n…®n avenemebam, gamiz…® mogh…®n paz…® n…® damigham. 
