\q2 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 35 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na g…®n amadagha ak…®rim na gasara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® uan inivaf…®zir agorogem ko tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazim bagh m…®zazim iniam.‚Äù 
\s1 God amizir kurar kamning gas…®ghas…®gham 
\p  
\v 36 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Ohola ko Oholiba akam aning gas…® aning tuis…®gh, aning amizir arazir kurar k…® aghuazibar gun aning m…®k…®m.  
\v 37 Aning amizir poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gamimning, egha gumazibav sozi me ariaghiri. Aning uaghan poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim, uan marvir guaba ko dagh ami. Aning na bagha boriba bate, egha me m…®suegha me isa aseba bagha ofa gami.  
\v 38 Aning arazir kamnangram amizir puvat…®. Aning nan d…®penim gamiz…® a bar m…®ze. Aning bar mogh…®ra Sabat…®n arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®gha aneb…®ragha ghaze, a pura dughiar k…®nim.  
\v 39 Aning uan boribav suagharigha da isa asebar ofa gamizir dughiar kamra, ua nan D…®penim…®n ghugha a gamiz…® a nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Aning nan D…®penim…®n arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zibagh ami.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 40 ‚ÄúAning zurara saghuiam…®n itir gumaziba bagha akaba amadima me izi. Ez…® aning ghua ruava uan damaziba agh…®va bis…®n aghuibar uaning…®n kurti.  
\v 41 Egha dabirabir bar aghuim gapera, ez…® aning…®n guamning…®n, me bizir aghuiba dakozim…®n da avara. Bizir aghuir me avezir kabar tong…®n, nan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim koma oliv…®n borer k…® me gan…®ngizim uaghan iti.  
\v 42 Ez…® aning orazi, gumazir av…®rim…®n n…®g…®nim oto. Gumazir igharagha garir av…®riba izi. Me marasi, wain…®n d…®paba apa onganizir gumazir kuraba, me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikegha ize. Ez…® amizir kamning, daveriaba uan agharibagh aghuigha atrivir dapanir asuar bar aghuimning uan dapanimning garu.  
\v 43 Ez…® k…® uab…® uab…® m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòAmizir kamning ti poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim gamua bar am…®raghama. Ez…® puvat…®, gumazir kaba ghua aning ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amuav…®ra iti.  
\v 44 Me zurara amizir kamning bagha ghua tuavim…®n amizim…®n arazim…®n m…®n aning gami. Ohola ko Oholiba, kar amizir arazir m…®z…®r…®zibagh amimning.  
\v 45 Aning arazir kurar poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim ko igharaz daraziv soaghar…®zir arazim gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, jas…®n arazir aghuibagh amiba, kotiam…®n aven aning…®n arazir kaba bagh aning ikuvighs…® aning…®n m…®k…®mam. Me fo, aning arazir kurar kabagh amima aning…®n dafariba ghuziba dar iti.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 46 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® m…®dorozir gumazir okoruatam…®n aku iz…®t…®, me pazav…®ra aning damut…® aning atiatight…® me aning…®n biziba okemegham.  
\v 47 Me dag…®abar aning giniv, m…®dorozir sababar aning ok…®va, aning…®n boribav sogh…®rarigh, aning…®n d…®penibar apongegham.  
\v 48 Eght…® nguazir kam…®n aven, k…® arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kam batuegham. Eght…® amiziba arazir kam…®n ganigh fogham, me aning…®n m…®n arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kabar amuan kogham.  
\v 49 Gumazamizir kaba, guan arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko asebar ziaba fer arazir kurar kaba bang…®n gua ikaragh, m…®zazim gua dan…®ngam. Eght…® gua kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam.‚Äù 
