\v 12 Kantrin kurar igharazibar adarazi iza, an okegha anetaghiz…®, a ir…®ghav iti. Ez…® an aguaba tintinibar m…®ghs…®aba ko danganir zaribar ire. Kantrin igharazibar gumazamizir an aguabar dughuazibar apengan itiba, anetegha igharagha ghue.  
\v 13 Eght…® kuaraziba iz…® temer ir…®zir kam gis…®n dapiam, eght…® as…®zir atiaba iz…® an aguabagh is…®n daruam.  
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…®va temer derav…®ra d…®pam isava aghuir ruaribagh amiba, ua puvat…®gham. Temeba bar ar…®ghiram, mati gumazamiziba ariaghira ghua Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n iti. 
