\v 7 \x - \xo 32:7 \xt Aisaia 13:10; Matyu 24:29; Mak 13:24-25; Luk 21:25; Akar Mogomem 6:12-13; 8:12\x*K…® n…® gas…®ghas…®ghamin dughiam…®n, 
