\v 24-25 ‚ÄúKantri Elam, ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra m…®dorozim…®n ariaghire. Ez…® an m…®dorozir gumazibar moziba bar an mozim okariz…®, a tong…®ra iti. Elamia God g…®fozir puvat…®gha, me angam…®ra ikiav…®ra ikia gumazamizir av…®rim gamiz…®, me aguava atiati. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n uaghira Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n ikia, gumazir aremezibar tong…®n ireghav ikia bar aghums…®ki. 
