\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God na m…®g…®a ghaze:  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® uan gumazamizibav k…®m suam: K…® apaniba amadaght…®, me kantrin tam…®n mang…®t…®, kantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba ti uan tav am…®seveght…®, a men nguazir m…®taghniam geghuv an ganamin gumazim…®n otogham.  
\v 3 A gant…®, apaniba iz…®t…®, a gumazamiziba fofoghs…® s…®gham giviam.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 33:4-5 \xt Ua Me Ini 9:19-21; Hibru 11:7\x*Eght…® gumazitam s…®gham…®n ikiangs…®zir ararem baregh…®va, ar…® mang…® uab…® mongan aghuaght…®, apaniba iz…®va a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Eght…® an ovevem…®n os…®mt…®zim, a uab…® a iniam.  
