\v 6 \x - \xo 33:6 \xt Aisaia 56:10-11; Esekiel 3:18; 18:20; 18:24\x*Eght…® eghuvir gumazitam apanibar gant…® me iz…®t…®, a ikiangs…®zim damu s…®gham giveraghan koght…®, apaniba iz…® gumazibav soght…® me ar…®ghiregham. Eght…® gumazamizir uan arazir kuraba ak…®rizir puvat…®gha ariaghire, kar men os…®mt…®zim puvat…®. Kar eghuvir gumazir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim, a ikiangs…®zim me gan…®ngizir puvat…®. 
