\v 7 \x - \xo 33:7 \xt Jeremaia 1:17; 26:2; Esekiel 3:17; Aposel 5:20\x*‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, nguazir kam…®n gumazim, k…® Israel…®n ik…®zim geghuvasa n…® am…®sefe. Ikiangs…®zir akar k…® n…® dan…®ngamiba, n…® oragh me m…®k…®m.  
