\v 9 \x - \xo 33:9 \xt Esekiel 3:19-21; Aposel 13:40-41; 13:46\x*Eght…® n…® ikiangs…®zir akam arazir kuram gamir gumazim m…®kemeght…®, a uan arazir kuraba atagh…®raghan aghuaght…®, an arazir kurar kam an ik…® a gas…®ghasight…® an aremegham. Eght…® n…® bizir kam…®n os…®mt…®zim puvat…®gham, egh n…® ovengan kogham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, arazir kurabagh amir gumazamiziba aremeghan an aghua 
\p  
\v 10 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® nan akam…®n gun Israel…®n ik…®zim m…®k…®m suam: Ia ghaze, e ak…®riba God gasaragha arazir kurar av…®ribagh amigha bar oseme, egha da bagha aghariba guni. E manmagh…®n angam…®ra ikiam?  
\v 11 \x - \xo 33:11 \xt 2 Samuel 14:14; Esekiel 18:23; 18:31; 2 Pita 3:9\x*N…® me m…®k…®m suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra ikia, egha k…® uan ziam…®n bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei: Arazir kurabagh amir gumazamiziba ariagh…®rima, nan navim derazir puvat…®. K…® kamaghsua, me arazir kuraba ategh angam…®ra ikiasa k…® ifonge. O Israel…®n ik…®zim, ia oragh! Arazir kurar ia amiba, ia da atakigh, egh ua na bagh iz…®. Ia tizim bagha ovengasa? 
\p  
\v 12 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israelia m…®k…®m suam, gumazir aghuim arazir kuram gami, an arazir aghuir a faragha amiziba an akuraghan kogham. Eght…® arazir kurabagh amir gumazim uan arazir kuraba ateght…®, k…® a gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. Eght…® gumazir aghuitam arazir kurabar amuam, egh an arazir aghuir a faragha amizibagh n…®ghn…®gh, da bang…®n nan damazim…®n deraghv…®ra ikian kogham. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 33:13 \xt Esekiel 3:20; 18:24\x*K…® gumazir aghuibav g…®a ghaze, me deraghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® gumazitam n…®ghn…®gh suam, an arazir aghuir an amiziba an akuraght…® a derav…®ra ikiam, egh arazir aghuiba ategh arazir kurabar amuam, eght…® k…® an arazir aghuir a fom…®rama amizibagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. A dat…®r…®gh…®n uan arazir kuraba bang…®n an aremegham.  
\v 14 Egh k…® gumazir kuraba me m…®k…®m suam, ia aremegham. Eght…® gumazir arazir kuram gamim, an ak…®rim ragh uan arazir kurabagh asaragh, egh arazir aghuibar amuam,  
\v 15 an aremeghan kogham. Egh a uan namakam da ikarvaghamin ababanim…®n m…®n inizir bizim, a uam a dan…®ngam. Egh an okemezir biziba a ua dar an…®ngam. Egh an arazir k…® ifongezir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim an…®dibar g…®nt…®gh aremeghan kogham, an angam…®ra ikiam.  
\v 16 An arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®ght…®, kamagh…®n k…® an arazir kuraba g…®n amadaght…® an angam…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEz…® n…®n gumazamiziba ghaze, arazir Ekiam amizir kam derazir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Men arazir me amibara derazir puvat…®.  
\v 18 Eght…® arazir aghuibagh amir gumazim, uan arazir aghuiba ategh arazir kurabar amu, egh da bang…®n ovegham.  
