\v 20 Ez…® Israel…®n ik…®zim, ia ghaze, arazir Ekiam amir kam a derazir puvat…®. K…® g…®n ia amir arazibara, da bagh vaghvagh ia tuis…®gham.‚Äù 
\s1 Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ikufi 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 33:21 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:3-10; Jeremaia 39:2-8; 52:4-14\x*E kalabuziabar m…®n itima, azenir namba 12 otoz…®, an iak…®nir namba 10…®n aven, an aruer namba 5…®n, Jerusalem…®n ikezir gumazir mam ara na bagha iza na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam, apaniba a inigha bar a gas…®ghas…®ki.‚Äù  
\v 22 Gumazir kam t…®ghar izamin guarat…®zir faragha zuim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim, am…®nim…®n m…®n nan m…®karzim…®n izi. Ez…® gumazir kam am…®mzaraghan m…®zaragharam oto. Ez…® dughiar kamra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua m…®k…®mamin gavgavim na gan…®ngi.\f + \fr 33:22 \ft N…® Esekiel 24:25-27…®n gan.\f* 
\s1 Gumazamizir kantri Israel ikiav…®ra itiba, me arazir kurabagh ami 
\p  
\v 23 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei,  
\v 24 O nguazir kam…®n gumazim, Israel…®n nguazim…®n itir danganir ikuvizibar ikiav…®ra itir gumazamiziba ghaze, Abraham a gumazir vam…®ra, ez…® nguazir kam bar mogh…®ra an anam. Ez…® e bar av…®rasemegha ghaze, ti guizbang…®ra, God nguazir kam e gan…®ngi.  
\v 25 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® me m…®k…®m suam: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: Ia ghuziba itir as…®ziba apav…®ra iti. Egha ia asebar ziaba fava gumazamiziba sozi me ariaghiri. Ia tizimsua ghaze, nguazir kam a ian nguazim?  
\v 26 Ia zurara m…®dorozibagh ami da otifi. Egha ia arazir kurar k…® aghuazibagh ami. Ia bar mogh…®ra poroghamiba uari bakeir arazibagh ami. Egha manmaghsua ia ghaze nguazir kam a iananam? Bar puvat…®, ia a inighan kogham. 
\p  
\v 27 ‚ÄúN…® me m…®k…®m suam: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra iti, k…® uan ziam…®n bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei: Danganir ikuvizibar ikiav…®ra itir gumazamiziba, apaniba iz…® me m…®sogh…®rar…®gham. Ez…® nguibabar azenan itir gumazamiziba, k…® as…®zir atiabar amut…®, da iz…® me m…®sogh me amam. Eght…® mogomer danganiba ko dag…®ar toribar moga iti darasi, ar…®mariar kuraba me damut…® me ar…®ghiram.  
\v 28 K…® nguazir kam damight…® a ikuvight…® gumazamiziba ko biziba an puvat…®gham. Egh k…® me damight…®, me uari fava amir ifaghatir arazim, a bar g…®vagham. Eght…® Israel…®n m…®ghs…®aba bar ruaribagh avagh, m…®temeght…® me dar aruan aghuagham.  
\v 29 Gumazamizir arazir kurar k…® aghuazibagh amiba, k…® pazav…®ra me damight…®, nguazim ikuvight…® gumazamiziba ko biziba an puvat…®gham. Eght…® me kamagh…®n ganigh fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazamiziba God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®nt…®zir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 30 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…®n gumazamiziba nguibar ekiam…®n d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n ikia, uan d…®penibar tiar akabar uari akuva ikia n…® g…®n…®ghn…®gha, kamagh…®n uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòIa iz…®. E mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n e m…®k…®mamin akaba baragham.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúNan gumazamiziba n…® m…®k…®mamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baraghasa, n…®n damazim…®n uari akuvagha apiaghav ti. Egha arazir n…® damuasa me m…®geiba, me dagh amir puvat…®. Me gumazamiziba uari isava akuava amir arazibagha amua, egha dag…®aba iniasav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha iti.  
\v 32 N…® kamagh…®n fogh, me n…®n akaba barazima, da mati gumazim amizim gifuegha uan gita m…®sogha, uan tiarir aghuim…®n ighiar aghuibagh ami. Ez…® me pura da baragha, dar g…®n mangan aghua.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 33:33 \xt 1 Samuel 3:20; Esekiel 2:5\x*Eght…® g…®n, n…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba guizbang…®n otivt…®, me kamagh…®n fogh suam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam men tong…®n iti.‚Äù 
\c 34  
\s1 God, Israelian gumazir dapanibar araziba tuis…®si 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israelian gumazir dapanibar atar ikuvighs…® me m…®k…®m suam: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei: Iavzika! Ia ivezir kuram iniam. Israelia mati sipsip…®n b…®zim, ez…® ia mati sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba. Ia uarira uarir akuaghapi. Egha ia uan sipsipbar akuaghapir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Ia sipsip…®n aghuir m…®karziba sara itibav sogha da apava, dar ar…®zibar ingarizir korotiabar uarir kurti. Egha ia dar akuaghapir puvat…®.  
\v 4 Ia sipsip…®n gavgaviba puvat…®ziba, deragha men garir puvat…®. Egha ar…®mariaba itiba, ia men ar…®mariaba agevima, me ua ghuamazir puvat…®. Egha duaba itiba, ia men duaba nozir puvat…®. Egha tintinibar zuiba, ia ua me isa izir puvat…®. Egha ovengeziba, ia me burir pu. Puvat…®. Ia uan gavgavim…®n dagh ativagha bar pazav…®ra dagh ami.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 34:5 \xt D…®boboniba 27:17; 1 Atriviba 22:17; 2 Eghaghaniba 18:16; Aisaia 56:9; Jeremaia 12:9; Matyu 9:36; Mak 6:34\x*Nan sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, da pura tintinibar zui, ez…® as…®zir atiaba dav sogha da api.  
\v 6 Nan sipsipba tintinibar arua m…®ghs…®abar ghuavanadi. Egha pura tintinibar nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar dar zui. Ez…® tav me bagha gara me burir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 7 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baragh:  
\v 8 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® zurara angam…®ra ikia mamagh…®ra iti, k…® uan ziam…®n bar guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei: Sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, as…®zir atiaba dav sogha da api. Nan sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba tong nan sipsipba burir puvat…®. Me deraghasa uarira uarir akuaghapi, egha sipsipbar akuaghapir puvat…®.  
\v 9 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia sipsipbagh eghuvir gumaziba, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam deragh a baragh:  
\v 10 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® ian apanim gami. K…® uan sipsipba ian dafariba dam ua da inigham, egh ia ateght…® ia ua sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazibar m…®n ikian kogham. Egh ia ua uarira uarir akuraman kogham. K…® uan sipsipba ian akatoriba da ua da inight…®, ia uam damamin sipsipba puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a uab…® sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazir aghuim 
\p  
\v 11 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa oragh. K…® uab…® uan sipsipba buriva ua me inigh iz…® deraghv…®ra men ganam.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 34:12 \xt Aisaia 40:11; Esekiel 30:3; Joel 2:2\x*Nan sipsipba tintinibar ghuegha, m…®tarmer ekiam…®n aven iti. Ez…® k…® gumazir dagh eghuvim…®n m…®n da akumakum da inigh izam.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 34:13 \xt Aisaia 65:9-10; Jeremaia 23:3; Esekiel 28:25\x*K…® kantrin igharazibar mang…® ua da inigh Israel…®n kantrin izam, kar dar nguazimra. Eght…® da m…®ghs…®aba ko faneba ko gumaziba itir danganibar borogh…®n ik…®, grazibar am…® deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 34:14 \xt Onger Akaba 23:2; Jeremaia 33:12\x*Egh da Israel…®n m…®ghs…®abar ik…®va grazir aghuibar amam. Da nguazir aghuim…®n ik…® avughs…® deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 15 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® ghaze, k…® uab…® uan sipsipbagh eghuv dar ganam. Egh k…® uab…® men aku aghuvsazir danganir aghuim…®n mangam.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 34:16 \xt Maika 4:6; Matyu 18:12-14; Mak 2:17; Luk 5:32\x*Eght…® nan sipsip…®n taba oveght…®, k…® mang…® da buri da bativ ua da inigh izam. Egh sipsip…®n tintinibar ghueziba, k…® ua dar aku izam. Eght…® taba ikuvigh duaba ik…®t…®, k…® dar duaba ak…®r da nogham. Eght…® taba ar…®mariaba ik…®t…®, k…® da ak…®right…® da ua ghuamaghegham. Egh sipsip…®n m…®karziba sara itiba ko sipsip…®n gavgaviba, k…® dagh as…®ghasigham. Guizbang…®ra, k…® guiz…®n arazim damu, egh sipsipbagh eghuv dar ganam.  
\v 17 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® vaghvagh ian araziba tuis…®gham, egh k…® sipsipba vong…®n dar ar…®gh, memeba vong…®n dar ar…®gham. 
\p  
\v 18 ‚ÄúIan marazi grazir aghuiba apava, naviba izefi, egha grazir ikiav…®ra itiba, ia pura da d…®ka da m…®rm…®ri. Ia d…®par d…®k…®riaba amegha g…®vagha, g…®n ia da d…®kab…®ra dagh amima, da nedi.  
\v 19 Ez…® nan sipsip…®n igharaziba, grazir ia d…®ka m…®rm…®riziba apava, d…®par ia d…®kab…®ri negariba api. Ian arazir kam, a bar ikufi. 
\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n ia m…®gei: Ia oragh! K…® vaghvagh ian araziba tuis…®gh ia tuiragham. Egh ia sipsip…®n gavgavir m…®karziba sara itiba k…® vong…®n ia ar…®gh, egh vong…®n sipsip…®n gavgaviba puvat…®zibar ar…®gham.  
\v 21 Ia sipsip…®n gavgaviba itiba, ia zurara sipsip…®n gavgaviba puvat…®ziba uan komba ko, uan dapaniba ko, uan namnabar da munamadima, da tintinibar zui.  
\v 22 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan sipsipba ia da da inight…®, ia ua pazav…®ra dar amuan kogham. K…® vaghvagh uan sipsipba tuis…®gh…®va sipsip…®n aghuiba vong…®n dar ar…®gh, egh sipsip…®n kuraba vong…®n dar ar…®gham. 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 34:23 \xt Akar Mogomem 7:17\x*‚ÄúK…® uan ingangarir gumazim Devit, an ik…®zim…®n gumazitam am…®seveght…®, a sipsipbagh eghuvir gumazim…®n ikiam. Egh a derav…®ra dar ganam.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 34:24 \xt Esekiel 37:24\x*Eght…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® men God…®n ikiam. Eght…® atrivitam, mati nan ingangarir gumazim Devit…®n m…®n me gativagh men ganam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 34:25 \xt Aisaia 11:6-9; Jeremaia 23:6; Hosea 2:18\x*Me navir am…®rizim…®n ik…® deragh dapiagh ik…®s…®, k…® me ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim damuam. Me m…®sogh…®rar…®ghamin as…®zir atiaba, k…® bar ada g…®vagham, eght…® da ua men nguazim…®n ikian kogham. Guizbang…®ra, nan sipsipba derav…®ra ik…®va ruarir ekiabar dakuam. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚ÄúK…® derav…®ra uan gumazamiziba ko nguazir nan m…®ghs…®am av…®nizibar amuam. Egh amozir dughiam…®n, k…® amozir av…®ribar amut…® da nguazim gir…® a damight…® a bar deragham.  
\v 27 Eght…® men azenibar itir temeba ov…®ziba ikiam. Eght…® azenibar dagheba otivam. K…® kantrin apanir nan gumazamiziba isa kalabuziabar m…®n me at…®zim, k…® kantrin kam…®n dafarim…®n ua me inigh izam. Eght…® me bar mogh…®ra uan nguazibar derav…®ra dapiagh ikiam. Egh dughiar kam…®n me fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 28 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba ua me ab…®nan kogham. Eght…® as…®zir atiaba ua me m…®sogh…®rarigh me aman kogham. Me derav…®ra ik…®t…®, tav ua me damut…® me atiatingan kogham. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúK…® men nguazim damut…®, dagheba bar derav…®ram an aghungam. Eght…® m…®tiriaba gumazamizibar azir arazim, a g…®vagham. Eght…® kantrin igharaziba ua me d…®povan kogham.  
\v 30 \x - \xo 34:30 \xt Esekiel 34:24; 37:27\x*Eght…® Israelia bar mogh…®ra fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God men God, egha me ko iti. Ez…® me nan gumazamiziba, me Israel…®n ik…®zim. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 34:31 \xt Onger Akaba 100:3; Jon 10:11\x*‚ÄúIa nan gumazamiziba, ia nan sipsipbar m…®n ikia, nan nguazimra iti. Ez…® k…® daghebar ian akuaghapa, ia geghuva, egha ian God…®n iti. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\c 35  
\s1 God Idomia gas…®ghasigham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 35:1-15 \xt Aisaia 34:5-17; 63:1-6; Jeremaia 49:7-22; Esekiel 25:12-14; Amos 1:11-12; Obadia 1:1-14; Malakai 1:2-5\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n gan…®va, Idom…®n kantri ikuvighs…® akam a gas…®va a m…®k…®m.  
\v 3 Egh gumazamizibav k…®m suam: 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam ghaze: 
\q2 N…® oragh! Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am, k…® n…®n apanim gami. 
\q1 K…® uan agharim n…®n nguazim…®n amadagh n…® damight…® n…® ikuvight…®, 
\q2 gumazamiziba ko biziba n…®n puvat…®ght…®, 
\q3 n…® pura ikiam. 
\q1  
\v 4 K…® n…®n nguibar ekiabar amight…® da ikuvight…®, 
\q2 gumazamiziba ko biziba dar puvat…®ght…®, da pura ikiam. 
\q3 Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\b  
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúIa Idomia fom…®ra Israelian apanim gami, egha k…® ivezir kuram me gan…®dir dughiam…®n, apaniba iza me m…®sozima, ia apanibar akuragha Israelia m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.  
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiar angam…®ra itim, k…® guizbang…®ra ghaze, apaniba ian ag…®nt…®gh ia m…®soght…®ma ia ar…®m…®ghiram. Ia fom…®ra gumazamizibav sozi me ariaghirir arazim…®n atiatingizir puvat…®, kamagh…®n amiz…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n apaniba ia m…®sueght…® ia ar…®mighiram.  
\v 7 K…® Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am damight…®, a danganir k…®nim…®n otoght…®, gumazamiziba ko biziba bar an puvat…®gham. Eght…® gumazamizir an mang…®gh zegh gamiba, k…® bar me kuavaremeght…®, me ua ikian kogham.  
\v 8 K…® n…®n gumazamizibar kuabar amut…®, da m…®ghs…®abar pura tintinibar ir…®v ikiam, egh uaghan danganir zariba ko daghurir dakeziba bar, men kuaba dagh izevegham.  
\v 9 K…® n…®n nguazim ko nguibar ekiabar amight…®, da pura ik…®t…®, gumazamiziba ko biziba ua dar aven ikian kogh kamagh…®ra ikiam. Eght…® ia fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Juda ko Israel…®n kantrin nguazimning, ian nguazimning, eght…® ia aning gativagham. Ez…® puvat…®, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® men God, k…® nguazir kamning…®n iti.  
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiar angam…®ra itim, k…® uan ziam…®n guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® ian arazir kuraba ikarvagham. Ia Israelian aghuagha men atara navir kuram men ikia pazav…®ra me gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® arazir kurar kabara ikarvagh, dar ivezir kuram is…® ia dan…®ngam. K…® tuavir kam…®n uab…® is…® Israelia akakaght…®, me nan arazir k…® ia gas…®ghas…®ghamim…®n gan…®va, derav…®ra na g…®fogham.  
\v 12 Eght…® ia Idomia kamagh…®n derav…®ra fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra God, k…® orazima, ia Israelian m…®ghs…®aba d…®pova akar kurabar kamagh…®n dav keme, ‚ÄòIsraelian m…®ghs…®aba ikuvigha bar g…®fa. Eght…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n kantrin kam inigh a gativagham.‚Äô  
\v 13 Ia Idomia puv ifaghata uari fa akar kurabar na m…®gei. K…® ian m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba baregha g…®fa.  
\v 14 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® bar mogh…®ra ia gas…®ghas…®ght…®, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n ganigh bar akongegham.  
\v 15 Nan gumazamiziba, Israel…®n ik…®zim, ikuvigha itir dughiam…®n ia bar akonge. Kamagh…®ra, ia Idomia, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n me batozir os…®mt…®zim…®n m…®rara bar mogh…®ra ia gas…®ghasigham. Eght…® Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am ko ian kantrin danganiba, da danganir bar ikuvizibar m…®n otogham. Eght…® Israelia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…®rara, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\c 36  
\s1 God derav…®ra Israelia damuam 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n na m…®gei: O nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® Israel…®n m…®ghs…®aba kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m: ‚ÄúO Israelian m…®ghs…®aba, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am baragh.  
\v 2 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: N…®n apaniba akam n…® gas…® suam, ‚ÄòBar dera! M…®ghs…®ar ekiar kaba dat…®r…®gh…®n e dar ghuaviba ikegham!‚Äô 
\p  
\v 3 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ikuvighs…® dav k…®m. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n m…®gei: Israel…®n borogh…®n itir kantriba iza, ia ek…®arugha ia ab…®nigha, ia gas…®ghasigha ia inigha kantrin igharazibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba ia d…®pova akar kurabar ia gasa ia m…®gei.  
\v 4 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, O Israel…®n m…®ghs…®aba, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa. Ian m…®ghs…®aba ko, daghuriba ko, danganir zariba ko, danganir as…®ghas…®ghiziba ko nguibar ekiar akaraghiregha biziba bar puvat…®ziba, kantrin igharazir Israel…®n borogh…®n itiba, ian biziba ok…®ava ia d…®pova akar kurabar ia m…®gei. 
\p  
\v 5 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei: K…® an…®ngagharir ekiam avim…®n m…®n, kantri Idom ko kantrin igharazibar ikia, pamtem ia m…®gei. Ia zurara navir averiar kuraba ikia bar akongegha ghaze, k…® pura bizim, egha nan nguazim ini. Egha nguazir kam…®n aven itir tuziba ko ruaribagh ifongegha uari bagh an biziba okemegha, dar ghuaviba ikiangi. 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® Israel…®n nguazim g…®n…®ghn…®gh a m…®k…®m suam: Ia m…®ghs…®aba ko daghuriba ko danganir zariba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, kamagh…®n ia m…®gei: Kantrin igharaziba ia d…®pova akar kurabar ia m…®gei, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan an…®ngagharir ekiam sara kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masava ami.  
\v 7 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam akam ak…®righa guizbang…®ra m…®g…®a ghaze, Israel…®n borogh…®n itir kantriba, me uaghan igharaz darazi d…®pov akar kurabar me m…®k…®mam. 
\p  
\v 8 ‚ÄúEght…® Israel…®n m…®ghs…®aba, ia gis…®n temeba ua mur…®va Israel…®n ik…®zim bagh uam ov…®ziba ituam. Me bar k…®ran oveghang…®n uamategh uan nguibabar izam.  
\v 9 O m…®ghs…®aba, k…® ia baghav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® deraghv…®ra ian gant…®, Israelia ian dagher azenibar ingaram.  
\v 10 K…® Israel…®n ik…®zim bar mogh…®ra me damight…®, me bar av…®rasemegh ian ikiam. Eght…® me ua nguibar ekiaba ko danganir men apaniba as…®ghas…®ghizibar ingaram.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 36:11 \xt Jeremaia 31:27; Esekiel 35:9; 37:6; 37:13\x*K…® ian itir gumazamiziba ko as…®ziba bar dar amight…®, dar d…®bobonim mavanangam. Ian d…®bobonim bar ghuavanaboght…®, gumazamiziba bar av…®rasemegham. K…® ia damight…®, gumazamiziba ian danganir m…®kebaba bar dar ikiam, mati ia fom…®ra ikez…® mogh…®n ikiam. Eght…® ian dabirabim bar deragham, egh ia fom…®ra ikez…® dabirabim bar a gafiragham. Eght…® ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.  
\v 12 Egh Israelia, nan gumazamiziba, k…® men aku mang…®t…® me ia dapiagh, derav…®ra ikiam. Egh me ian ghuaviba ikegham. Eght…® ia men nguazibar m…®n ikiam. Egh ia ua men boribagh as…®ghs…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Gumazamizir maba ghaze, ‚ÄòEn nguazir kam, a gumazamiziba api, egha a guizbang…®ra en boribagh as…®ghas…®si.‚Äô  
\v 14 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mangam, ia ua gumazamizibar aman kogham, egh ia uan boribagh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.  
\v 15 Eght…® kantrin igharaziba, Israel…®n m…®ghs…®aba d…®pova akar kurabar ua ia m…®k…®man kogham. Ia m…®ghs…®aba dat…®r…®gh…®n, ua men aghums…®zir akaba baraghan kogham. Egh ia ua uan kantrin gumazamizibar amut…®, me arazir kuram bang…®n ir…®ghan kogham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\s1 God Israelia gamiz…®,  // me gumazamizir igiabar oto 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan akam isa na gan…®ga ghaze,  
\v 17 ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazim, Israel…®n ik…®zim uan nguazim…®n itir dughiam…®n, me arazir bar m…®z…®r…®zibagh amua, nguazir kam gas…®ghas…®ki. Me mati, amizim uan iak…®nir ar…®mariabagh amua nan damazim…®n m…®ze.  
\v 18 Me gumazir av…®rim m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me marvir guabar ziaba fe, egha uan nguazim gamiz…®ma, a nan damazim…®n bar m…®ze. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® uan an…®ngagharim me gingegha, ivezir kuram isa bar me gan…®ngi.  
\v 19 K…® men arazir kurar me amizir kaba tuisigha da ikarvagha me batoghez…®, me tintinibar kantrin igharazibar ghue.  
\v 20 Me tintinibar ghuez…®, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba men garima, me nan ziar bar zuezim gas…®ghas…®gha ghaze, a pura ziar k…®nim. Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba ghaze, ‚ÄòKar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarasi. A me gamiz…®, me an nguazim ategha g…®fa.‚Äô  
\v 21 Ez…® k…® fo, Israelia ghuezir danganiba bar, kantrin kabar gumazamizibar tong…®n nan ziar bar zuezim d…®povava a gas…®ghas…®gha ghaze, a pura ziar k…®nim. Ez…® k…® uan ziam bagha oseme. 
\p  
\v 22 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® akar kam Israel…®n ik…®zim dan…®ngigh: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®g…®a ghaze: Ia kantribar gumazamizir igharazibar tong…®n itima, me ian gara nan ziar bar zuezim d…®pova a gas…®ghas…®gha ghaze, a pura ziar k…®nim. Bizir gavgavir k…® damuamin kaba, ia Israel…®n ik…®zim, k…® ia g…®n…®ghn…®gha dagh amir pu. Bar puvat…®. K…® uan ziar ekiam baghav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha dar amuasa.  
\v 23 K…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, Ia Israelia, ia Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar tong…®n, nan ziar ekiam gas…®ghas…®gha ghaze, a pura ziar k…®nim. Eght…® k…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar amight…®, me ganigh fogh suam, k…® uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ez…® nan arazir k…® ia gamiba, da bar mogh…®ra zue. Eght…® me ziar ekiam na dan…®ngam. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 36:24 \xt Aisaia 43:5-6; Esekiel 34:13; 37:21\x*‚ÄúBizir k…® ia damuamin kam a kamak…®n, k…® kantrin ia dat…®r…®gh…®n itibar, bar ia inigh iz…® ua ian nguazimra ia ar…®gham.  
\v 25 Egh d…®par d…®k…®riam inigh, ian dapanibagh is…®n a kavamang ian arazir kuraba batueght…®, ia nan damazim…®n bar zuegham. Egh ian arazir kurar ia marvir guaba fem bagh, ia rueght…® ia zuegham.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 36:26 \xt Sekaraia 7:12\x*\x - \xo 36:26-28 \xt Esekiel 11:19-20\x*Egh k…® ian navir averiabar amight…® da ua igiabar otivigham. Egh duar igiam ia dat…®gham. Ian naviba faragha dag…®abar m…®n gavgafi. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian navir kuraba batuegh n…®ghn…®zir igiam is…® ian navir averiabar ar…®gham.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 36:27 \xt Esekiel 11:20; 37:14\x*Egh k…® uan duam is…® ia dan…®ngam, eght…® a ian navir averiabar ikiam. Egh ia f…®t…®, ia deraghv…®ra arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemezibar g…®n mangam.  
\v 28 Egh ia nguazir k…® fom…®ra ian inazir afeziabagh an…®ngizir kam…®n ikiam. Egh ia nan gumazamizibaram otoght…®, k…® ian God…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 29 ‚ÄúK…® ian akuragh ia damut…®, ia ua nan damazim…®n arazir m…®z…®r…®zibar amuan kogham. K…® ian dagher azenibar amight…®, da dagher av…®riba ikiam. Eght…® dagheba otevir dughiaba ua ia bativan kogham.  
\v 30 K…® ian temer bebar amight…®, da ov…®zir bar av…®riba ik…® bar av…®rasemegham. Eght…® dagheba otevir dughiaba ua ia bativan kogham. Eght…® ia Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar damazim…®n uam aghums…®ghan kogham.  
\v 31 Egh ia uan arazir kurar ia amiziba ko arazir m…®z…®r…®zir k…® aghuazibagh n…®ghn…®gham. Egh arazir kurar kaba bang…®n, ia uari dar aghuagh…®va bar aghums…®gham. 
\p  
\v 32 ‚ÄúO Israel…®n ik…®zim, ia kamagh…®n fogh, k…® ian akurvaghasa arazir kabagh amir pu. Puvat…®, k…® uan ziar ekiam g…®n…®ghn…®gha dagh ami. K…® kamaghsua, k…® arazir kabar amut…®, ia uan arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®gh bar osemegh aghums…®gham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 33 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® ian arazir kuraba batueght…® ia zueghamin dughiam…®n, k…® ia ateght…® ia ua uan nguibar ekiabar ik…®va, ua danganir ian apaniba as…®ghas…®ghizibar ingaram.  
\v 34 Gumazamiziba faragha ian nguazir ikuvizibagh arua dar garima, da pura ikia bar m…®temegha ruarir ekiabar m…®n gari. Eght…® k…® dar amight…®, ia ua dar ingar…®va oparam.  
\v 35 Eght…® me bar suam, manmagh amiz…®, nguazir kam faragha pura ikia ruarir ekiar m…®tiam…®n m…®n gari, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n, a derav…®ram oto, mati Iden…®n azenim. Manmagh amiz…®, nguibar ekiar me akara as…®ghas…®ghizir bar ikuviziba, Israelia dat…®r…®gh…®n ua dar ingarigha, vaghvagha da av…®nigha d…®vazir gavgavibar ingari. Ez…® gumazamizir bar av…®rim vaghvagha uam adar aven iti.  
\v 36 Eght…® kantrin ian borogh…®n ikiav…®ra itiba fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® uab…® nguibar ekiar ikuviziba, k…® ua dar ingari. Egha nguazir pura itiba, k…®rara uam ada opari. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n damuasa Akar Gavgavim gami. Guizbang…®ra, k…® dar amuam. 
\p  
\v 37 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: K…® Israel…®n ik…®zim ua men amamangat…®ght…®, me uarir akurvaghs…® ua nan azangs…®gham. Eght…® k…® me damight…®, men gumazamiziba sipsip…®n okoruar mam…®n m…®n, bar av…®rasemegham.  
\v 38 Me Jerusalem…®n ofa damuasa inigha izir sipsipbar m…®n, me bar av…®rasemegham. Eght…® Israelia ua ingaramin nguibar ekiar kabagh iz…®vagham. Eght…® me kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\c 37  
\s1 Esekiel gumazamizibar agharir av…®rim…®n gari 
\p  
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gavgavim nan izez…®, an Duam na inigha ghua danganir zarir mam…®n na at…®. Danganir kam, gumazamizibar agharir av…®riba an iti.  
\v 2 Egha a na inigha, ga ghua danganir zarir kam garua, agharir pozir bar av…®rim…®n garima, agharir kaba bar m…®sigha ireghav iti.  
\v 3 Ez…® a kamagh…®n nan azara, ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, agharir kaba, da ua gumazamizibar m…®n otivigh angam…®ra ikiam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® k…® a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, n…® uab…®ra fo, k…® fozir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan akar kam agharir kabav k…®m suam: Ia agharir m…®diariba, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia nan akam baragh.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 37:5 \xt Onger Akaba 104:30\x*K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n agharir kabav gei: K…® am…®nim ia dan…®ngam, eght…® ia ua gumazamizibar m…®n otivigh angam…®ra ikiam.  
\v 6 K…® ag…®riba ko tuziba ia dar…®gh, egh m…®karzir inim…®n ian ag…®riba ko tuzir kaba avegham. Egh k…® ia damight…® ia gumazamizibar m…®n otivight…®, k…® am…®nim ia danight…® ia angam…®ra ikiam. Eght…® ia deraghv…®ra fogh suam, k…® uab…® k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® k…® a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amua, akam akurav…®ra ikia orazima, Maia! N…®g…®nir dafar kuram oto. K…® oraghav…®ra itima, aghariba t…®ngazi. Egha k…® garima, aghariba uamategha uan danganibara ghua uariv tifi.  
\v 8 Egha g…®n k…® ag…®riba ko tuzibar garima, da uam agharibar poke, ez…® dar m…®karziba otivigha da avara. Ez…® me gumazamizibar m…®n otifi, ez…® am…®nim men aven ghuzir puvat…®. 
