\v 10 \x - \xo 37:10 \xt Akar Mogomem 11:11\x*Ez…® k…® an akar kam akurima, am…®nim m…®karzir kuar kabar aven zuima, me angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim inigha, bar mogh…®ra tuifi. Me gumazamizir bar av…®rim oto. Ez…® men d…®bobonim bar ghuavanabo. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® a kamagh…®n na m…®gei, ‚ÄúNguazir kam…®n gumazim, Israel…®n ik…®zim, mati agharir m…®s…®ngizibar m…®n aremez…® mogh…®n iti. Egha me zurara ghaze: En aghariba m…®sigha g…®fa. E ua deraghv…®ra ikian kogham. Egh e bar g…®vagham.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® nan akam me m…®k…®nasa k…® ifonge, egh kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m suam: O nan gumazamiziba, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® ian gumazir kuaba afezir mozibagh kuigh, ia inigh azenan izegh, egh ia inigh ua Israelian nguazim…®n mangam, kar ian nguazim.  
