\v 14 \x - \xo 37:14 \xt Esekiel 36:27\x*Egh k…® uan Duam ia danight…®, ia angam…®ra ikiam. Eght…® k…® ua ian aku ian nguazimra mangam, eght…® ia an ik…® deraghv…®ra ikiam. Eght…® k…® kamagh…®n damuamin dughiam…®n, ia deraghv…®ra fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n damuasa Akar Gavgavim gami. Guizbang…®ra, k…® dar amuam.‚Äù 
\s1 Israelia kantrin vam…®ran otogham 
\p  
\v 15 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua na m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúO nguazir kam…®n gumazim, n…® ter araritam inigh akar kam…®n an osirigh: ‚ÄòKar Judan adarazi ko Israelian igharazir me ko itiba, men ter ararim.‚Äô Egh n…® ter ararir igharazitam inigh akar kam…®n an osirigh, ‚ÄòKar Josep…®n adarasi, me Efraim…®n anabam…®n gumazamiziba ko Israelian me ko iti adarazir ter ararim.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 17 ‚ÄúEgh n…® ter ararir kamning…®n ruaghatevimning uaghara uan dafarim…®n aning…®n suiragh, egh aning isafuraght…®, aning ter ararir vam…®ran m…®n ik…®.  
\v 18 Eght…® n…®n gumazamiziba n…®n azaragham, bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim manmak…®n?  
