\p  
\v 20 ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim…®n osizirim itir ter ararimning uaghara aning…®n suiraght…®, gumazamiziba aning…®n ganam.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 37:21 \xt Esekiel 36:24\x*Eght…® n…® me m…®k…®m suam: K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Israelia ghua kantrin igharazibar tong…®n itibar aven, k…® me akuvagh, me inigh ua men nguazim…®n izam.  
\v 22 K…® me damight…® me kantrin vam…®ran otogh uan nguazim…®n ikiam. Eght…® Israel…®n m…®ghs…®abar p…®n, atrivir vam…®rara me gativagh men ganam, eght…® me bighan kogh ua kantrin pumuning…®n ikian kogham.  
\v 23 Me ua aseba ko bizir k…® aghuazibar ziaba fan kogh, nan damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. Egh arazir kurabar amuan kogham. K…® men akuragh arazir kurar me amibar me f…®right…®, me ua uarigh as…®ghas…®ghan kogham. K…® me damight…® me nan damazim…®n zuegham. Dughiar kam…®n, me nan gumazamizibar ik…®t…®, k…® men God…®n ikiam.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 37:24 \xt Esekiel 34:24\x*Eght…® nan ingangarir gumazim Devit, an ik…®zim…®n tong…®n gumazitam men atrivim…®n ikiam. Me bar uari inigh atrivir vam…®ran apengan ik…®t…®, a uab…®ra me geghuvam, mati sipsipba geghuvir gumazim derav…®ra uan sipsipbagh eghufi. Dughiar kam…®n, me deraghv…®ra arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa me m…®kemezibar g…®n mangam.  
\v 25 Me nguazir k…® uan ingangarir gumazim Jekop gan…®ngizim…®n aven ikiam. Kar nguazir men inazir afeziaba ikezim. Me uan boriba ko men g…®n otivamin ovavir boriba, me zurara nguazir kam…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Nan ingangarir gumazim, Atrivim Devit, an ik…®zim…®n gumazitam me gativagh men gan mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 26 K…® me ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim damight…® a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. Me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n g…®n mang…® navir am…®rizim ko dabirabir aghuim ikiam. Eght…® k…® derav…®ra me damuam. K…® me damight…®, me ek…®va bar av…®rasemegham. Egh k…® uan D…®penim men tong…®n anet…®ght…®, a ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 37:27 \xt 2 Korin 6:16; Akar Mogomem 21:3\x*Nan D…®penim men tong…®n ik…®t…®, k…® men God…®n ik…®t…®, me nan gumazamizibar ikiam.  
\v 28 Nan D…®penim zurara men tong…®n ikiam, eght…® kantriba bar kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® Israelia ginaba, eght…® me na baghv…®ra ikiam.‚Äù 
