\v 4 \x - \xo 38:4 \xt Aisaia 43:17; Esekiel 39:2; Daniel 11:40\x*K…® n…® damight…® n…® igh…®gh…®regham, eght…® n…® ko n…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba bar, k…® akezibar ian aghozibar aghuigh, ia gekuigh ia inigh mang…®gham. N…®n hoziaba, ko hoziabagh is…®n apiaghiri gumaziba, ko m…®dorozir gumazir uan m…®dorozir biziba ateriba, ko m…®dorozir gumazir oraba ko m…®dorozir sabar itir bar av…®rim, k…® bar ia gekuigh ia inigh mangam.  
