\v 7 \x - \xo 39:7 \xt Esekiel 36:20; 38:16; 38:23\x*‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n damight…®ma, nan gumazamiziba Israelia, nan ziar bar zuezim g…®fogham. K…® ua uan ziar bar zuezim damight…®, me uam aghums…®zim na dan…®ngan kogh, egh kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, a pura bizim. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n bar zuezim. 
