\v 8 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® ghaze: Dughiar k…® m…®kemezim, a k…®ran oveghang…®n otogham. Bar guizbang…®ra, dughiar kam zuam…®ram otoght…®, k…® bizir kabar amuam.  
\v 9 Gumazamizir Israel…®n nguibar ekiabar aven itiba, me uan nguibaba ategh mang…® m…®dorozir bizir apaniba pura taghiz…® itiba iniam. Kar men oraba ko, barir piba ko, barir afuziba ko, afuzir ruariba ko, m…®dorozir ifaniba. Me dazibar m…®n dar avibar ar…®gh mang…® 7plan azenibar tugham.  
\v 10 Egh me ua 7plan azenir kabar ua ruariba ko, tuzibar dazibar kuan kogham. Me avibar ar…®ghs…® m…®dorozir bizir kabar ik…®ziba ater mang…® dar avibar ar…®gham. Gumazir men biziba okemeziba, Israelia kamagh…®ra, me ikaragh men biziba okemegham. Apanir men bizibagh as…®ghas…®ghiziba, Israelia uaghan me ikaragh men bizibagh as…®ghas…®gham. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®keme.‚Äù 
