\v 11 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBizir kaba bar otivight…®ma, k…® Israel…®n nguazim…®n Gok af…®s…® nguazim a danigham. Danganir kam, Amangs…®zim Itir D…®par Akarem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n danganir zarim…®n ikiam, egh gumazamizir mang…®gh izegh gamibar tuavim ap…®righam. Me g…®n Gok uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, danganir zarir kam…®n bar me afam. Egh me ziar kam a dar…®gham, ‚ÄòGok…®n M…®dorozir Gumazibar Danganir Zarim.‚Äô  
\v 12 Israel…®n ik…®zim, 7plan iak…®nibar gumazir kuaba afir ingangarim damu mang…® g…®vaght…®, nguazim ua deragh zuegham.  
