\v 14 Me gumaziba am…®seveght…®, me mang…® nguazim daru gumazir kuar nguazim…®n ikiav…®ra itiba buri, da is…® mozibar afam. Me kamagh…®n damight…®, nguazim ua zuegham. Me 7plan iak…®nibar kamagh…®n kuaba buriamin ingangarim damuam.  
\v 15 Me Israelian nguazim…®n averiam zurara mavanabogh…®n iz…®ghir…®gh damuva agharitabar apigh, egh ifevim damigh ababanim…®n m…®n dar borogh…®n anesaragham. Eght…® gumazir kuaba afiba iz…®, agharir kaba inigh mang…® Gok…®n M…®dorozir Gumazibar Danganir Zarim…®n dar afam.  
