\v 23 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, k…® Israel…®n ik…®zim gamizir bizir m…®ngarim g…®fogham. Dughiar kam…®n Israelia nan akam batuegha arazir kurabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me kantrin igharazim…®n kalabuziabar m…®n ghue. Ez…® k…® ak…®rim ragha me gasaragha me ataghiz…®ma, apaniba me ab…®ra m…®dorozibar me m…®soghar…®ki.  
\v 24 Me arazir m…®z…®r…®zir bar kurabagh ami. Ez…® k…® ak…®rim ragha me gasaraz…®, me uan arazir kurar kabar ivezim ini. 
