\v 25 ‚ÄúK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ekiam, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Jekop…®n ovavir borir kantrin igharazibar kalabuziabar m…®n itiba, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n men apangkuvigh ua me inigh, men ik…®zim damight…® me ua deragham. Egh k…® uan ziar zuruzim deragh an gant…®, gumazitam aneb…®raghan kogham.  
\v 26 Israelia ua deraghv…®ra uan nguazim…®n ik…®t…®, gumazitam ua me damut…®, me atiatingan kogham. Egha me faragha ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha amizir arazir kurabagh n…®ghn…®gh, aghums…®zir ekiam iniam.  
\v 27 K…® apanibar kantribar tong…®n ua uan gumazamiziba inigh izam. Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, k…® Israelia gamizir bizir kam…®n ganigh fogh suam, nan araziba bar zuegha dera.  
